ing%20took%20place%2C%20the%20government%20survived%20by%20a%2014-vote%20margin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20year%20later%20there%20were%20allegations%20that%20six%20MPs%20from%20the%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%2C%20including%20party%20stalwart%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Shibu%20Soren%2C%20had%20taken%20bribes%20to%20vote%20for%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20at%20the%20time%20the%20court%20held%20that%20the%20lawmakers'%20immunity%20from%20prosecution%20extended%20to%20votes%20and%20speeches%20in%20the%20House%3B%20this%20was%20under%20Article%20105%20and%20Article%20194%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EJMM%20Leader%20Sita%20Soren's%20Challenge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202012%2C%20the%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha's%20Sita%20Soren%20(Shibu%20Soren's%20daughter-in-law)%2C%20who%20was%20accused%20of%20taking%20a%20bribe%20to%20cast%20a%20vote%20in%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20election%2C%20claimed%20immunity%20citing%20the%201998%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-sets-up-7-judge-bench-to-reconsider-its-1998-verdict-involving-mps-4423241%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20To%20Reconsider%201998%20Verdict%20On%20MPs'%20Immunity%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jharkhand%20High%20Court%20dismissed%20her%20appeal%2C%20and%20that%20dismissal%20was%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20challenged%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20top%20court%2C%20in%20September%20last%20year%2C%20agreed%20to%20reconsider%20its%201998%20judgment%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20an%20important%20issue%20having%20a%20significant%20bearing%20on%20%26quot%3Bmorality%20of%20polity%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Did%20Supreme%20Court%20Say%20Today%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20extensive%20hearings%2C%20the%20top%20court%20final%20said%20that%20a%20claim%20for%20immunity%20in%20such%20situ