%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jayshetty.me%2Fabout-jay%5C%22%3EJay%20Shetty's%20official%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20his%20school%20years%2C%20Jay%20Shetty%20spent%20vacations%20living%20with%20monks%20in%20India%2C%20immersing%20himself%20in%20their%20wisdom%20and%20teachings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20report%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Flifeandstyle%2Fng-interactive%2F2024%2Ffeb%2F29%2Fjay-shetty-self-help-empire%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E%20claims%20that%20Mr%20Shetty%2C%20author%20of%20the%20bestselling%20book%20'Think%20Like%20A%20Monk%3A%20Train%20Your%20Mind%20for%20Peace%20and%20Purpose%20Every%20Day'%2C%20falsely%20claimed%20to%20have%20spent%20three%20years%20in%20a%20temple%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2036-year-old%2C%20who%20was%20born%20in%20London%20and%20went%20to%20business%20school%2C%20hosts%20the%20%E2%80%9COn%20Purpose%E2%80%9D%20podcast%2C%20wherein%20he%20has%20welcomed%20guests%20like%20Michelle%20Obama%2C%20Kim%20Kardashian%20and%20the%20late%20Kobe%20Bryant%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20runs%20the%20Jay%20Shetty%20Certification%20School%2C%20where%20%26quot%3Bstudents%20pay%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20to%20learn%20the%20Jay%20Shetty%20discipline%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20investigative%20report%20casts%20doubt%20on%20the%20accuracy%20of%20Mr%20Shetty's%20own%20narrative%20and%20educational%20qualifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20graduating%2C%20Shetty%20forgoes%20a%20life%20of%20material%20success%20to%20live%20as%20a%20monk%20himself.%20Three%20years%20later%2C%20he%20has%20another%20revelation%3A%20his%20purpose%20in%20life%20is%20not%20to%20live%20the%20humble%20life%20of%20a%20monk%20but%20to%20use%20his%20preternatural%20oratory%20skills%20to%20share%20wisdom%20with%20the%20world.%20Thus%20begins%20his%20transformation%20into%20a%20public%20self-help%20personality%20and%20his%20swift%20rise%20to%20fame.%20Shetty's%20success%20is%20largely%20predicated%20on%20this%20riches-to-rags-to-riches%20backstory.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20alleged%20that%20Mr%20Shetty%20also%20misrepresented%20certain%20aspects%20of%20his%20biography%2C%20including%20the%20story%20about%20how%20his%20life%20was%20changed%20at%20the%20age%20of%2018%20when%20he%20heard%20a%20lecture%20by%20a%20monk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20Mr%20Shetty's%20resume%20includes%20a%20degree%20in%20behavioural%20science%20from%20a%20business%20school%20that%20doesn't%20even%20offer%20the%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20claimed%20that%20Mr%20Shetty%20uses%20his%20spiritual%20identity%20to%20make%20huge%20sums%20of%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CShetty%20is%20hardly%20the%20first%20self-help%20guru%20to%20embellish%20his%20spiritual%20credentials%20to%20amass%20followers%2C%20but%20he%20demands%20huge%20sums%20of%20money%20for%20his%20guidance.%20Shetty%20has%20used%20his%20spiritual%20authority%20to%20launch%20a%20number%20of%20subscription%20and%20education%20services%2C%20including%20the%20life-coaching%20school%2C%20which%20charges%20%247%2C400%20a%20term%20for%20%E2%80%9CPostgraduate%20Diploma%20(Level%207)%20qualifications%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20equivalent%20to%20a%20master's%20degree.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20his%20association%20with%20the%20Hare%20Krishna%20movement%2C%20Mr%20Shetty%20has%20been%20reportedly%20reserved%2C%20possibly%20due%20to%20controversies%20surrounding%20the%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShetty%20avoids%20mentioning%20Iskcon%2C%20instead%20describing%20himself%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9CVedic%20monk%E2%80%9D%2C%E2%80%9D%20stated%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20must%20be%20noted%20that%20Jay%20Shetty%20has%20been%20battling%20with%20accusations%20of%20plagiarism%20for%20years%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20stated%