rachud%2C%20and%20Justices%20A.S.%20Bopanna%2C%20M.M.%20Sundresh%2C%20P.S.%20Narasimha%2C%20J.B.%20Pardiwala%2C%20Sanjay%20Kumar%2C%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%2C%20have%20overturned%20the%20%3Cem%3EPV%20Narasimha%20Rao%3C%2Fem%3E%20order%20of%2026%20years%20ago%20in%20which%20a%20five-judge%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20held%20that%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%20could%20claim%20immunity%20for%20bribes%20under%20Articles%20105(2)%20and%20194(2)%20of%20the%20constitution.%20Such%20lawmakers%20would%20be%20immune%20from%20prosecution%20if%20they%20upheld%20their%20end%20of%20the%20bargain%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-mps-mlas-bribe-vote-speech-legislature-claim-immunity-251136%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20noted%20the%20earlier%20order%20as%20having%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202012%2C%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20leader%20Sita%20Soren%20was%20accused%20of%20accepting%20a%20bribe%20for%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20vote%20and%20claimed%20immunity%20under%20Article%20194(2).%20When%20the%20Jharkhand%20high%20court%20dismissed%20her%20plea%2C%20Soren%20challenged%20it%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20which%20heard%20the%20case%20in%20October%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20judgment%20in%20%3Cem%3EPV%20Narasimha%20Rao%3C%2Fem%3E%20which%20grants%20immunity%20from%20prosecution%20to%20a%20member%20of%20a%20legislature%20who%20has%20allegedly%20engaged%20in%20bribery%20for%20casting%20a%20vote%20or%20making%20a%20speech%20has%20wide%20ramifications%20on%20public%20interest%2C%20probity%20in%20public%20life%2C%20and%20parliamentary%20democracy.%20There%20is%20a%20grave%20danger%20of%20this%20court%20allowing%20the%20error%20to%20be%20perpetuated%20if%20the%20decision%20were%20not%20reconsidered%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20observed%20that%20it%20was%20disagreeing%20the%20overruling%20the%20earlier%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20said%20that%20the%20offence%20of%20bribery%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Corruption%20Act%20is%20%E2%80%9Ccomplete%E2%80%9D%20the%20moment%20a%20bribe%20is%20taken%20and%20cannot%20depend%20on%20whether%20the%20receiver%20makes%20good%20on%20the%20promise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCorruption%20and%20bribery%20of%20members%20of%20the%20legislature%20erode%20the%20foundation%20of%20Indian%20parliamentary%20democracy.%20It%20is%20disruptive%20of%20the%20aspirations%20and%20deliberative%20ideals%20of%20the%20constitution%20and%20creates%20a%20polity%20which%20deprives%20citizens%20of%20a%20responsible%2C%20responsive%2C%20and%20representative%20democracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20also%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20enthusiastically%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1764541405140009405%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Ewelcomed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20judgment%20with%20an%20all-caps%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Eswagatam%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%20or%20%E2%80%98welcome%E2%80%99%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20great%20judgment%20by%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Supreme%20Court%20which%20will%20ensure%20clean%20politics%20and%20deepen%20people%E2%80%99s%20faith%20in%20the%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20party%2C%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20has%20however%20been%20criticised%20for%20engineering%20defections%20in%20various%20states%20like%20Karnataka%2C%20Goa%2C%20Manipur%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709536366000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F25132016%2FSupreme-court4.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-sets-aside-1998-ruling-no-immunity-for-lawmakers-accepting-bribe-for-votes-speeches%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'There%20is%20a%20grave%20danger%20of%20this%20court%20allowing%20the%20error%20to%20be%20perpetuated%20if%20the%20decision%20were%20not%20reconsidered%2C'%20the%20CJI-led%20bench%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-sets-aside-1998-ruling-no-immunity-for-lawmakers-accepting-bribe-for-votes-speeches%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BGambhir%20Got%20Carried%20Away%26quot%3B%3A%20On%20Spat%20With%20Kohli%2C%20Naveen's%20Big%20Revelation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20on-field%20spat%20between%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Naveen-ul-Haq%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107680-naveen-ul-haq-playerprofile%5C%22%3ENaveen-ul-Haq%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20also%20involved%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gautam%20Gambhir%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F563-gautam-gambhir-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGautam%20Gambhir%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20became%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20talking%20points%20of%20IPL%202023.%20The%20incident%20took%20place%20during%20the%20IPL%20match%20between%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bangalore%20and%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20at%20the%20Ekana%20Stadium%20in%20Lucknow.%20The%20argument%20began%20between%20Kohli%20and%20Naveen%20but%20it%20quickly%20turned%20into%20a%20nasty%20spat%20as%20LSG%20mentor%20Gambhir%20intervened%20in%20support%20of%20the%20Afghanistan%20pacer%20and%20both%20former%20India%20teammates%20locked%20horns%20against%20each%20other.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver-since%20the%20incident%20took%20place%2C%20all%20the%20three%20players%20who%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20spat%2C%20have%20shared%20their%20views%20regarding%20it.%20Recently%2C%20Naveen%20shared%20some%20inside%20details%20about%20the%20infamous%20fight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20went%20to%20play%20our%20away%20match%20in%20Bengaluru.%20That's%20where%20it%20all%20started.%20We%20won%20that%20game%20-%20it%20was%20very%20close%20%E2%80%93%20so%20one%20of%20our%20players%20%5B%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Avesh%20Khan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64916-avesh-khan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAvesh%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E%5D%20threw%20the%20helmet%20in%20excitement%20after%20scoring%20the%20winning%20runs.%20Virat%20Kohli%20probably%20didn't%20like%20it.%20Next%2C%20their%20team%20came%20to%20Lucknow.%20I%20think%20I%20went%20out%20to%20bat%20at%20No.%209%20or%2010%20and%20we%20had%20pretty%20much%20lost%20the%20game%20by%20then%2C%26quot%3B%20Naveen%20said%20in%20a%20podcast%20with%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwSDKvoyQe4c%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EZalmi%20TV%3C%2Fi%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20I%20didn't%20expect%20that%20I%20would%20be%20sledged.%20But%20when%20it%20happened%2C%20like%20I%20said%2C%20when%20someone%20starts%2C%20I%20can't%20hold%20back.%20After%20the%20game%2C%20things%20continued%20during%20the%20handshake%20too.%20The%20sledging%20came%20from%20two%20guys%20%E2%80%93%20Kohli%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mohammed%20Siraj%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107503-mohammed-siraj-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMohammed%20Siraj%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Kohli%20and%20Gambhir%20have%20an%20history%20of%20sharing%20heated%20moments%20in%20IPL.%20Earlier%20in%20IPL%202013%2C%20Kohli%20got%20into%20a%20heated%20argument%20against%20Gambhir%2C%20who%20was%20the%20captain%20of%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20Gambhir's%20involvement%20in%20his%20fight%20against%20Kohli%2C%20Naveen%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BGautam%20Gambhir%20got%20carried%20away%20%5Bwith%20the%20shush%20gesture%5D%20because%20in%20the%20previous%20game%2C%20when%20we%20needed%201%20off%201%2C%20one%20of%20their%20bowlers%20wanted%20to%20run%20the%20non-striker%20out%20while%20running%20in%20to%20bowl.%20It%20was%20the%20last%20wicket.%20It%20got%20heated%20because%20the%20bowler%20missed%20taking%20the%20bails%20off.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSpirit-wise%20it%20wasn't%20looking%20good%20because%20it%20had%20proven%20to%20be%20such%20a%20good%20game%20by%20then.%20It%20would%20have%20been%20a%20shame%20had%20it%20ended%20in%20a%20run%20out.%20Because%20of%20that%2C%20he%20wanted%20to%20silence%20the%20crowd.%20He%20is%20a%20passionate%20guy%2C%20and%20so%20is%20Virat%2C%26quot%3B%20Naveed%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20during%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20in%20October%2C%20both%20Kohli%20and%20Naveen%20resolved%20their%20differences%20and%20were%20seen%20hugging%20each%20other.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709536320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Foe3ue2gg_virat-kohli-and-gautam-gambhir_625x300_02_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-got-carried-away-naveen-ul-haq-recalls-on-field-ipl-spat-with-virat-kohli-5172129%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20on-field%20spat%20between%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20Naveen-ul-Haq%2C%20which%20also%20involved%20Gautam%20Gambhir%2C%20became%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20talking%20points%20of%20IPL%202023%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BGreat%20Judgment%26quot%3B%3A%20PM's%20Post%20On%20No%20Immunity%20To%20MPs%2C%20MLAs%20In%20Bribery%20Cases%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20praised%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20verdict%20today%20that%20said%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%20do%20not%20enjoy%20immunity%20from%20prosecution%20for%20taking%20bribe%20to%20make%20a%20speech%20or%20cast%20a%20vote%20in%20the%20legislature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E