%20turned%20himself%20in%20at%20the%20Clackamas%20County%20Jail.%20This%20was%20after%20a%20grand%20jury%20issued%20an%20indictment%2C%20accusing%20Mr%20Michael%20of%20multiple%20felonies%20and%20misdemeanours%20stemming%20from%20last%20year's%20sleepover%20on%20August%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20stated%20that%20the%20officials%20didn't%20speculate%20on%20any%20motive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20probable%20cause%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oregonlive.com%2Fclackamascounty%2F2024%2F02%2Flake-oswego-dad-accused-of-drugging-girls-at-sleepover.html%5C%22%3Eaffidavit%20obtained%20by%20Oregon%20Live%3C%2Fa%3E%20confirmed%20that%20Mr%20Michael%20mixed%20mango%20smoothies%20with%20benzodiazepine%2C%20and%20served%20it%20to%20his%20daughter's%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20benzodiazepine%20is%20a%20depressant%20that%20slows%20the%20nervous%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oregonlive.com%2Fclackamascounty%2F2024%2F02%2Flake-oswego-dad-accused-of-drugging-girls-at-sleepover.html%5C%22%3EOregon%20Live%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20charges%20being%20faced%20by%20Mr%20Michael%20include%20causing%20another%20person%20to%20ingest%20a%20controlled%20substance%20and%20application%20of%20a%20controlled%20substance%20to%20the%20body%20of%20another%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Michael's%20lawyer%2C%20Mark%20Cogan%20has%20reportedly%20stated%20that%20he%20hadn't%20seen%20any%20evidence%20in%20the%20case.%C2%A0Mr%20Cogan%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CMr%20Meyden%20is%20presumed%20innocent%20and%20we%20hope%20that%20people%20will%20reserve%20judgment%20until%20all%20of%20the%20facts%20and%20circumstances%20are%20known.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20the%20emergency%20room%20at%20Randall%20Children's%20Hospital%20at%20Legacy%20Emanuel%20in%20Portland%2C%20three%20girls%20tested%20positive%20for%20benzodiazepine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NY%20Post%20report%20stat