Ethnic%20Democracy%3Cem%3E%2C%20said%2C%20was%20different%20from%20a%20deep%20state.%20The%20lines%20between%20what%20happens%20officially%20and%20what%20happens%20unofficially%20and%20even%20illegally%20are%20blurred.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJaffrelot%20notes%20in%20the%20interview%20that%20India%20has%2C%20under%20Modi%2C%20become%20%E2%80%9Ca%20landscape%20of%20very%20worrying%20divisions%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20full%20text%20of%20the%20interview%20is%20provided%20below.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20lightly%20for%20style.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKaran%3C%2Fb%3E%20%3Cb%3EThapar%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Hello%20and%20welcome%20to%20a%20special%20interview%20for%20The%20Wire.%20With%20Narendra%20Modi%20having%20completed%2010%20years%20as%20prime%20minister%2C%20and%20with%20the%20forthcoming%20elections%20suggesting%20that%20he%20could%20win%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term%2C%20we%20ask%20how%20should%20we%20assess%20his%20legacy%2C%20and%20secondly%20how%20should%20we%20assess%20his%20political%20personality%3F%20Joining%20me%20for%20today%E2%80%99s%20discussion%20is%20one%20of%20the%20great%20scholars%20of%20Indian%20politics%2C%20professor%20of%20south-Asian%20politics%20both%20at%20Sciences%20Po%20in%20Paris%2C%20as%20well%20as%20King%E2%80%99s%20College%20in%20London%2C%20and%20author%20of%20%E2%80%98Modi%E2%80%99s%20India%3A%20Hindu%20Nationalism%20and%20the%20rise%20of%20ethnic%20democracy%E2%80%99%2C%20Christophe%20Jaffrelot.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EProfessor%20Jaffrelot%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20been%20Prime%20Minister%20for%2010%20years%2C%20and%20he%20hopes%20to%20add%20another%205%20at%20the%20forthcoming%20elections%2C%20so%20let%20me%20start%20by%20asking%3B%20what%20is%20your%20assessment%20of%20his%20performance%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20over%20the%20last%20decade%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChristophe%3C%2Fb%3E%20%3Cb%3EJaffrelot%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Well%20I%20would%20say%20that%20it%20is%20very%20contrasted%20and%20that%20at%20one%20end%20India%20has%20become%20very%20visible%20on%20the%20international%20scene%2C%20although%20it%20abstains%20most%20of%20the%20time%20in%20the%20UN%2C%20but%20on%20the%20other%20end%20India%20is%20back%20to%20the%20kind%20of%20deviations%20it%20experienced%20before%20and%20during%20Indira%20Gandhi%20in%20particular.%20Communal%20conflicts%20have%20intensified%2C%20with%20the%20minorities%20being%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%2C%20the%20north-south%20divide%20being%20very%20deep%20again%2C%20and%20not%20to%20say%20anything%20about%20Manipur%2C%20Ladakh%2C%20Kashmir%2C%20and%20new%20divisions%20have%20been%20activated%2C%20or%20re-activated%20based%20on%20caste%3B%20look%20at%20the%20Marathas%20mobilisation%2C%20and%20class%3B%20look%20at%20the%20farmers%20movement%2C%20so%20the%20scene%2C%20the%20national%20scene%20is%20a%20landscape%20of%20divisions.%20And%20a%20statesman%2C%20especially%20in%20a%20country%20that%20has%20experienced%20Partition%20like%20India%2C%20is%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20unity%20of%20the%20nation%2C%20and%20therefore%20I%20would%20say%20yes%3B%20the%20contrast%20between%20the%20international%20dimension%20and%20the%20domestic%20scene%20is%20very%20striking%20to%20me.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20How%20worrying%20are%20the%20divisions%20that%20you%E2%80%99ve%20identified%3B%20I%20noticed%20that%20you%E2%80%99ve%20identified%20multiple%20divisions%3B%20not%20just%20Hindu-Muslim%2C%20not%20just%20North-South%2C%20but%20also%20rich-poor%2C%20how%20worrying%20are%20these%20divisions%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECJ%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20They%20are%20very%20worrying%20because%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20really%20move%20forward%20without%20being%2C%20without%20having%20everybody%20on%20board.%20Without%20a%20minimum%20consensus%20on%20what%20the%20nation%20should%20be%20and%20do%3B%20for%20instance%20the%20way%20the%20southern%20states%20are%20now%20so%20resentful%20of%20the%20way%20the%20north%20is%2C%20well%20%E2%80%98taking%20their%20money%E2%80%99%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20a%20cause%20for%20concern%2C%20and%20this%20concern%20will%20certainly%20intensify%20if%20the%20re-delimitation%20is%20made%20according%20to%20the%20coming%20census%2C%20undermining%20the%20representation%20of%20the%20south%20in%20the%20parliament.%20You%20know%2C%20these%20issues%20have%20to%20be%20taken%20care%20of%20very%20carefully%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20only%20one%20of%20the%20many%20divisions%20that%20I%E2%80%99ve%20mentioned%3B%20the%20north-east%20of%20course%20is%20another%20huge%20challenge.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FsGRQOR0P4c8%3Fsi%3DkqxH9lDPddrwuLZM%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20I%E2%80%99ll%20just%20underline%20for%20the%20audience%20your%20description%20of%20India%3B%20%E2%80%98a%20landscape%20of%20very%20worrying%20divisions%2C%20and%20there%20are%20multiple%20divisions%E2%80%99.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20talk%20a%20little%20about%20some%20of%20the%20things%20that%20Mr%20Modi%20has%20done%20during%20the%20last%2010%20years%3B%20he%20frequently%20boasts%20about%20his%20handling%20of%20the%20economy%3B%20he%20says%20has%20made%20India%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20fifth%20biggest%20economy%2C%20and%20has%20lifted%20250%20million%20out%20of%20poverty.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%20his%20critics%20talk%20about%20unprecedented%20levels%20of%20unemployment%2C%20increased%20inequality%20and%20K-shaped%20growth.%20What%E2%80%99s%20your%20opinion%20of%20how%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20handled%20the%20economy%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECJ%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Well%2C%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20claims%20on%20the%20economic%20front%20are%20simply%20not%20supported%20by%20the%20few%20data%20we%20still%20have.%20And%20here%20I%20must%20underline%20that%20as%20a%20scholar%20working%20in%20India%20for%2040%20years%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20really%20struggling%20to%20get%20data%E2%80%A6%20official%20data%20used%20to%20be%20a%20goldmine%20for%20the%20students%20of%20India%2C%20and%20now%20we%20are%20missing%2C%20badly%20missing%2C%20the%20census.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20since%201881%20the%20census%20has%20not%20taken%20place%2C%20and%20we%20also%20have%20the%20NSS%20survey%2C%20measuring%20the%20level%20of%20poverty%3B%20that%20was%20on%20the%20rise%20by%20the%20way%20when%20the%20survey%20was%20released%2C%20in%20fact%20leaked%2C%20in%202019.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Futtar-pradesh-exams-cancellations-protests%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOver%252010%2520lakh%2520aspirants%2520had%2Cmere%252067%252C000%2520police%2520constable%2520jobs.%5C%22%3EMore%20Cancellations%2C%20Over%2050%20Lakhs%20Affected%2C%20Cloud%20Over%20Boards%20Too%3A%20The%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Exam%20Story%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20we%20do%20not%20have%20as%20much%20official%20data%20as%20we%20used%20to%2C%20but%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20data%20we%20still%20have%2C%20we%20can%20somewhat%20say%20that%20on%20the%20economic%20front%2C%20this%20decade%20is%20a%20quasi-loss%20decade.%20Of%20course%20not%20for%20oligarchs%20and%20full%20of%20people%20including%2C%20of%20course%20Gautam%20Adani%2C%20who%20have%20prospered%2C%20but%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20SMEs.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJoblessness%20remains%20very%20high%2C%20especially%20among%20the%20youth%2C%20especially%20among%20the%20educated%20urban%20youth%2C%20which%20is%20very%20paradoxical.%20The%20inflation%20rate%20remains%20also%20high%2C%20whereas%20the%20savings%20and%20investments%20keep%20falling%3B%20the%20decline%20of%20investments%20in%20India%20is%20very%20disturbing%2C%20because%20if%20you%20do%20not%20invest%2C%20how%20can%20you%20prepare%20for%20the%20future%3F%20And%20in%20that%20regard%20we%20have%20also%20a%20very%20mixed%20%E2%80%98Make%20in%20India%E2%80%99%20program%20reserves%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20the%20success%2C%20it%20has%20not%20been%20as%20successful%20as%20anticipated.%20Look%20at%20the%20urban-rural%20divide%2C%20why%20are%20farmers%20up%20in%20arms%20again%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBecause%20the%20terms%20of%20trade%20continue%20to%20impoverish%20them.%20And%20as%20a%20result%20you%20have%20dominant%20castes%2C%20like%20Marathas%2C%20asking%20for%20reservation%2C%20they%20want%20to%20be%20recognised%20as%20Backward%20Classes.%20Is%20this%20the%20way%20forward%3F%20And%20positive%20discrimination%20policies%20at%20large%20are%20under%20attack%3B%20not%20only%20a%20quota%20has%20been%20created%20for%20the%20upper%20class%20under%20the%20economically%20weaker%20sections%20tag%2C%20but%20the%20shrinking%20of%20the%20public%20sector%20means%20that%20jobs%20reserved%20for%20Dalits%2C%20Adivasis%2C%20OBC%E2%80%99s%2C%20are%20also%20less%20numerous.%20So%20the%20K-shaped%20growth%20means%20more%20inequalities%20indeed.%20And%20if%20you%20go%20by%20the%20data%20of%20Thomas%20Piketty%2C%C2%A0%20you%20see%20that%20India%20is%20now%20the%20most%20unequal%20country%20in%20the%20world%20after%20South%20Africa%2C%20a%20country%20that%20has%20inherited%20the%20legacy%20of%20apartheid.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20I%20would%20say%2C%20and%20I%20would%20close%20on%20this%2C%20that%20was%20the%20plan%3B%20the%20plan%20was%20to%20retain%20social%20hierarchies%2C%20the%20plan%20was%20to%20diffuse%20caste%20mobilisation%20by%20Dalits%20and%20OBCs.%20Hindutva%20is%20a%20response%20to%20Mandal%2C%20Hindutva%20is%20the%20antidote%20to%20plebian%20mobilisations%2C%20the%20idea%20is%20while%20your%20enemies%20are%20not%20upper%20caste%20but%20the%20Muslims%2C%20Hindus%20have%20to%20close%20rank%20against%20this%20threat%20posed%20by%20Muslims%2C%20and%20in%20the%20process%20elite%20groups%20defend%20the%20existing%20order%2C%20social%20order.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Would%20I%20be%20right%20in%20concluding%20from%20that%20answer%20that%20other%20than%20oligarchs%2C%20large%20suedes%20of%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%20have%20either%20not%20prospered%20or%20they%20have%20stagnated.%20You%20mentioned%20SMEs%2C%20you%20mentioned%20joblessness%20for%20youths%2C%20farmers%2C%20Dalits%2C%20Adivasis%2C%20together%20that%E2%80%99s%20probably%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20country%2C%20and%20they%20have%20not%20experienced%20either%20growth%2C%20or%20they%20have%20stagnated%20under%20Modi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECJ%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Yes%2C%20the%20urban%20middle%20class%20has%20of%20course%20benefited%20from%20this%20policy.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20supply%20side%20policy%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20pro-rich%20policy%20clearly.%20You%20look%20at%20the%20fiscal%20tax%20system%2C%20it%20has%20systematically%20reformed%2C%20to%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20rich%20and%20mostly%20upper-middle%20class%20people%2C%20not%20the%20salaried%20of%20course.%20Incidentally%20that%20is%20the%20Gujarat%20model%2C%20this%20is%20exactly%20what%20I%20show%20in%20my%20latest%20book%20%3Cem%3EGujarat%20under%20Modi%3A%20Laboratory%20of%20Today%E2%80%99s%20India%3C%2Fem%3E.%20That%20was%20exactly%20what%20we%20saw%20for%2013%20years%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20and%20it%20has%20been%20replicated.%20Incidentally%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20history%20of%20India%20that%20an%20original%20model%20can%20be%20scaled%20up%20at%20a%20national%20and%20even%20semi-continental%20level.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20remarkable%20achievement%20in%20a%20way.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20212830%2FNarendra-Modi-Jammu-February-2024-1024x512.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20212830%2FNarendra-Modi-Jammu-February-2024-1024x512.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20212830%2FNarendra-Modi-Jammu-February-2024-300x150.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20212830%2FNarendra-Modi-Jammu-February-2024-800x400.png%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20212830%2FNarendra-Modi-Jammu-February-2024.png%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698053%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22420%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EScreenshot%20from%20X%2F%40narendramodi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Now%20Modi%20dominates%20the%20Indian%20political%20horizon%20and%20there%20is%20a%20huge%20personality%20cult%20that%20surrounds%20him.%20He%20oddly%20refers%20to%20himself%20in%20the%20third%20person%2C%20and%20often%20his%20ministers%2C%20including%20our%20former%20Vice-President%20of%20the%20country%2C%20compare%20him%20to%20God.%20His%20policies%20are%20called%20%E2%80%98Modi%20guarantees%E2%80%99.%20Is%20all%20of%20this%20understandable%20and%20justified%20because%20he%20is%20popular%2C%20or%20does%20it%20smack%20of%20megalomania%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECJ%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Well%20such%20a%20personality%20cult%20is%20a%20classic%20by-product%20of%20populist%20politics.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20it%20under%20Erdo%C4%9Fan%20in%20Turkey%2C%20Orb%C3%A1n%20in%20Hungary%2C%20Bolsonaro%20in%20Brazil%2C%20Trump%20in%20the%20US%2C%20most%20of%20the%20populist%20leaders%20are%20megalomaniacs.%20When%20they%20win%20elections%20they%20claim%20that%20the%20whole%20country%20is%20behind%20them.%20And%20again%20that%20is%20what%20Modi%20used%20to%20say%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20%E2%80%9860%20million%20Gujaratis%20are%20behind%20me%E2%80%99%2C%20today%20%E2%80%981.4%20billion%20Indians%20are%20behind%20me%E2%80%99.%20And%20they%20claim%20that%20they%20are%20the%20country%2C%20they%20are%20the%20nation%2C%20and%20they%20attempt%20almost%20naturally%20after%20that%20to%20prevail%2C%20to%20concentrate%20all%20the%20poor%20in%20their%20hands%20and%20to%20dominate%20all%20the%20institutions.%20Indira%20Gandhi%20followed%20the%20same%20pattern%2C%20%E2%80%98India%20is%20Indira%2C%20and%20Indira%20is%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20Modi%20is%20no%20exception%2C%20except%20that%20in%20his%20case%20the%20people%20he%20claims%20to%20embody%20are%20only%20made%20of%20the%20Hindu%20community%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20we%20call%20majoritarianism.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20And%20secondly%20in%20contrast%20to%20Indira%20who%20could%20only%20use%20the%20radio%2C%20he%20relies%20on%20new%20technologies%2C%20he%20can%20saturate%20the%20public%20sphere%20by%20using%20the%20television%20of%20course%2C%20social%20media%2C%20holograms%20in%20the%20past.%20And%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20could%20be%20compared%20to%20God%20by%20the%20Vice%20President%20of%20India%20is%20not%20so%20surprising%20because%20only%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echamchas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20survive%20politically%20in%20this%20regime.%20What%20is%20more%20remarkable%20is%20that%20Narendra%20Modi%20himself%20believes%20in%20this%20idea.%20According%20to%20what%20he%20told%20to%20Ranjan%20Mukhopadhyay%2C%20and%20this%20is%20not%20so%20surprising%3B%20Imran%20Khan%20also%20believes%20today%20that%20he%20has%20received%20a%20mandate%20from%20God%2C%20not%20the%20same%20one%20of%20course%2C%20but%20you%20have%20this%20clear%20attempt%20by%20national%20populists%20to%2C%20yes%2C%20become%20megalomaniacs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Very%20quickly%2C%20is%20his%20personality%20cult%20bigger%20than%2C%20worse%20than%2C%20more%20worrying%20than%20Indira%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%3F%20Because%20of%20the%20new%20technologies%2C%20and%20also%20because%20he%20is%20focusing%20only%20on%20the%20Hindus%20and%20not%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECJ%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Yes%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20difficult%20to%20compare%20two%20evils%2C%20but%20certainly%20you%20have%20a%20qualitative%20difference%20here%20in%20the%20sense%20that%2C%20yes%20there%20is%20an%20ideology%20behind%2C%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20had%20no%20ideology.%20The%20Hindu%20Rashtra%20is%20definitely%20the%20goal%2C%20so%20that%E2%80%99s%20a%20big%20difference%2C%20that%20makes%20a%20big%20difference.%20And%20secondly%2C%20yes%20the%20means%2C%20the%20resources%20are%20much%20more%20systematically%20used%20for%20communication%2C%20for%20even%20the%20criss-crossing%20of%20society.%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20had%20a%20very%20poor%20organisation%20behind%2C%20you%20know%20the%20Congress%20party%20could%20never%20be%20a%20cadre-based%20party.%20Narendra%20Modi%20can%20rely%20on%20activists%2C%20all%20kinds%20of%20activists%3B%20not%20only%20the%20Sangh%20Parivar%20activists%20but%20those%20who%20pay%20allegiance%20to%20him%20personally.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Now%20side%20by%20side%20with%20the%20personality%20cult%20and%20his%20larger%20than%20life%20image%2C%20is%20his%20style%20of%20governance.%20How%20would%20you%20characterise%20his%20handling%20of%20institutions%20like%20parliament%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20the%20judiciary%2C%20security%20agencies%20like%20the%20enforcement%20directors%20and%20the%20CBI%2C%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20everything%20is%20now%20run%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20office%2C%20not%20by%20members%20of%20his%20cabinet%20or%20ministers%20of%20the%20government.%20He%20believes%20he%20has%20deepened%20Indian%20democracy%2C%20his%20critics%20accuse%20him%20of%20authoritarianism%2C%20what%E2%80%99s%20your%20opinion%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3ECJ%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Well%20again%2C%20we%20have%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20modus%20operandi%20of%20the%20populist.%20He%20claims%20he%20represents%20the%20people%2C%20he%20is%20the%20people%2C%20he%20relates%20directly%20to%20his%20people%2C%20so%20the%20legitimacy%20he%20gets%20from%20this%20claim%20helps%20him%20to%20short%20circuit%20all%20the%20institutions.%20You%20know%20parliament%20hardly%20matters%20in%20this%20context%20because%20he%20represents%20the%20people%2C%20and%20all%20the%20MPS%20elected%20by%20the%20people%20for%20BJP%20have%20been%20nominated%20by%20him%20himself.%20The%20party%20itself%20is%20redundant%2C%20you%20know%20the%20BJP%20used%20to%20be%20a%20carrier%20based%20party%20with%20strong%20state%20leaders%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20gone%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20over.%20They%20are%20parachuted%20from%20New%20Delhi%2C%20most%20of%20them%2C%20and%20those%20who%20were%20strong%20enough%20with%20the%20base%20have%20been%20side-lined.%20and%20yeah%20parliament%20is%20a%20bit%20stumped.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20is%20more%20surprising%20is%20the%20way%20the%20judiciary%20as%20an%20institution%20finally%20succumbed%20to%20pressure.%20and%20again%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20so%20surprising%20that%20they%20tried%20to%20reform%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%2C%20remember%20Orb%C3%A1n%20did%20it%20in%20Hungary%2C%20Kaczy%C5%84ski%20did%20it%20in%20Poland%2C%20Netanyahu%20is%20trying%20hard%20to%20do%20it%20in%20Israel.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20compete%20with%20the%20legality%3B%20I%20have%20the%20legitimacy%2C%20how%20can%2C%20how%20c