%20even%20the%20judiciary%20has%20resisted%20all%20the%20institutions%20have%20been%20somewhat%20undermined%2C%20certainly%20we%20can%20argue%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20has%20recently%20declared%20that%20the%20election%20bonds%20were%20unconstitutional%2C%20but%20before%20that%20they%20had%20upheld%20so%20many%20decisions%20regarding%20Ayodhya%2C%20Article%20370%2C%20other%20seen%20as%20a%20money%20Bill%2C%20the%20dilution%20of%20RTI%2C%20the%20up-hauling%20of%20UAPA%2C%20and%20they%20are%20sitting%20on%20the%20CAA%20for%20four%20years%20now.%20So%20we%20really%20have%20um%20a%20judiciary%20that%20is%20not%20what%20we%20used%20to%3B%20remember%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20was%20the%20most%20powerful%20judiciary%20in%20the%20world%2C%C2%A0%20and%20admired%20across%20the%20globe.%20One%20last%20Point%20about%20the%20ED%20used%20against%20the%20opposition%2C%20in%20order%20to%20intimidate%20its%20leaders%2C%20in%20order%20to%20co-opt%20them%20more%20easily.%20this%20is%20really%20an%20era%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eaaya%20ram%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20you%20know%20there%20is%20no%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Egaya%20ram%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20there%20are%20only%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eaaya%20ram%E2%80%99s%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20not%20only%20because%20of%20corruption%20but%20also%20because%20of%20fear.%20And%20this%20sentiment%2C%20fear%20has%20neutralised%20Mayawati%2C%20has%20pushed%20so%20many%20congress%20leaders%20in%20the%20arms%20of%20BJP%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20very%20sophisticated%20way%20to%20undermine%20the%20opposition%2C%20and%20Congress%20especially.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20A%20thought%20occurred%20to%20me%20as%20I%20heard%20your%20answer%3B%20he%20has%20subjugated%20and%20reduced%20to%20subordinates%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20parliament%2C%20judiciary%2C%20security%20agencies.%20Is%20he%20the%20most%20powerful%20prime%20minister%20India%20has%20ever%20had%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECJ%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Oh%20yes%2C%20oh%20yes%2C%20remember%20Nehru%20who%20ruled%20for%2017%20years%2C%20and%20who%20seemed%20to%20be%20the%20king%2C%20in%20a%20way%2C%20of%20India%2C%20he%20had%20to%20write%20a%20letter%20to%20Chief%20ministers%20every%2015%20days%3B%20to%20consult%20them%2C%20to%20build%20consensus%20on%20each%20and%20every%20issue%2C%20and%20he%20could%20not%20resist%20them.%20he%20could%20not%20resist%20them%20when%20they%20asked%20for%20re-delimitation%20of%20the%20Indian%20states%20borders%20according%20to%20the%20linguistic%20criterion%2C%20he%20was%20not%20for%20it%20but%20he%20had%20to%20do%20it%2C%20because%20Congress%20was%20a%20pyramid%20made%20of%20pyramids%2C%20and%20you%20had%20to%20follow%20what%20the%20state%20bosses%20had%20to%20say.%20Today%2C%20where%20is%20the%20BJP%20state%20boss%20in%20a%20position%20to%20resist%20anything%20Narendra%20Modi%20would%20decide%3F%20Even%20demonetisation%20was%20decided%20without%20consulting%20any%20chief%20minister%2C%20including%20BJP%20chief%20ministers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20One%20deep%20concern%2C%20and%20you%E2%80%99ve%20hinted%20at%20it%20in%20your%20earlier%20answers%2C%20is%20the%20sharp%20divide%20that%E2%80%99s%20emerged%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims.%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20vigorously%20deny%20that%20such%20a%20divide%20exists%2C%20but%20many%20people%20believe%20that%20in%20fact%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20are%20responsible%20for%20it%2C%20what%E2%80%99s%20your%20view%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECJ%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20No%20certainly%2C%20BJP%20is%20largely%20responsible%20for%20this%20divide%20because%20it%20plays%20the%20polarisation%20card%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20based%20on%20communal%20riots%20for%20years.%20Again%20the%20Gujarat%20pogrom%20in%202002%2C%20that%20was%20followed%20by%20the%20dissolution%20of%20the%20assembly%20and%20elections%20to%20benefit%20from%20polarisation%2C%20was%20the%20model.%20But%20I%20would%20say%20that%20BJP%20is%20not%20the%20only%20actor%20we%20need%20to%20factor%20in%20there%2C%20you%20know.%20Vigilantes%20are%20also%20very%20much%20responsible%20for%20this%20divide%2C%20and%20I%20think%20we%20need%20to%20pay%20more%20attention%20to%20the%20groundwork%20they%20are%20doing%20against%20what%20they%20call%20love%20jihad%2C%20or%20land%20jihad%2C%20or%20for%20reconversion%20to%20Hinduism%2C%20or%20for%20cow%20protection.%20These%20campaigns%20resulting%20in%20dozens%20of%20lynching%E2%80%99s%2C%20all%20shown%20on%20social%20media%20for%20impacting%20the%20Muslim%20minority%20even%20more.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F16123640%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-06-16-at-12.25.23-PM-1024x768.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F16123640%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-06-16-at-12.25.23-PM-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F16123640%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-06-16-at-12.25.23-PM-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F16123640%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-06-16-at-12.25.23-PM.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-658503%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20shop%20where%20a%20poster%20on%20%E2%80%98love%20jihad%E2%80%99%20had%20been%20pasted.%20Photo%3A%20Atul%20Ashok%20Howale%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20know%20this%20is%20what%20I%20call%20a%20deeper%20state%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20only%20the%20state%20that%20is%20at%20work%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20only%20the%20official%20BJP%20ruled%20apparatus%2C%20state%20apparatus%2C%20but%20at%20the%20social%20level%2C%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%2C%20a%20kind%20of%20cultural%20policing%20of%20a%20new%20kind%20that%20makes%20the%20state%20almost%20redundant.%20of%20course%2C%20you%20have%20many%20joint%20ventures%20with%20vigilante%E2%80%99s%20and%20police%2C%20in%20UP%20or%20Haryana%20doing%20the%20job%20together%2C%20but%20in%20many%20cases%20Vigilantes%20are%20on%20their%20own%2C%20and%20they%20are%20the%20new%20police%20creating%20a%20de%20facto%20Hindu%20Rashtra.%20Well%20you%20may%20say%20de%20facto%20becomes%20the%20de%20jure%20the%20moment%20you%20have%20the%20CAA%20as%20a%20new%20law%2C%20and%20new%20laws%20also%20making%20conversions%20very%20difficult%2C%20inter-religious%20marriages%20very%20difficult%2C%20but%20I%20really%20insist%20on%20keeping%20together%20what%20is%20done%20officially%2C%20from%20what%20is%20done%20unofficially%2C%20and%20even%20illegally.%20But%20again%20we%20find%20the%20legitimacy%20question%3B%20vigilantes%20are%20doing%20something%20legitimate%2C%20even%20they%20defend%20a%20secret%20cause%20because%20of%20Hindutva%2C%20and%20it%20may%20be%20illegal%2C%20nobody%20will%20go%20against%20that.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20You%20know%2C%20you%20said%20something%20that%20I%20think%20is%20particularly%20new%20and%20important-%20you%20said%20India%20has%20a%20deeper%20state%2C%20and%20this%20is%20different%20to%20the%20front%20facade%20of%20the%20official%20state.%20That%20there%20is%20a%20distinction%20between%20what%20happens%20officially%2C%20and%20what%20happens%20unofficially%2C%20and%20even%20illegally.%20A%20deeper%20state%20is%20terminology%20we%E2%80%99re%20used%20to%20associating%20with%20Pakistan%2C%20where%20the%20military%20establishment%20is%20the%20deeper%20state%2C%20and%20the%20civilian%20politicians%20is%20the%20facade.%20But%20you%E2%80%99re%20suggesting%20something%20akin%2C%20not%20similar%20but%20akin%2C%20is%20happening%20here%3B%20there%20is%20the%20S%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eangh%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Parivar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20vigilantes%2C%20the%20cow%20lynchers%2C%20who%20are%20part%20of%20the%20deeper%20state%2C%20there%20are%20the%20BJP%20civilian%20politicians%20that%20are%20the%20front%20facade.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECJ%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20your%20deeper%20state%20is%20different%20from%20a%20deep%20state%3B%20indeed%20a%20deep%20state%20is%20largely%20associated%20with%20intelligence%20services%2C%20who%20are%20acting%20behind%20the%20curtain%2C%20and%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20mean%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20there%20in%20India%20also.%20But%20a%20deeper%20state%20is%20different%20because%20it%20has%20a%20societal%20dimension%3B%20the%20state%20is%20there%20but%20relates%20and%20protect%2C%20people%20who%20are%20doing%20the%20cultural%20policy%20in%20at%20the%20societal%20level%2C%20making%20sure%20that%20Muslim%20boys%20do%20not%20talk%20to%20Hindu%20girls%20on%20the%20University%20campuses%20or%20elsewhere%2C%20making%20sure%20that%20XY%20any%20Hindu%20will%20not%20sell%20any%20land%20or%20any%20house%20to%20a%20Muslim%20at%20the%20local%20level.%20This%20is%20the%20way%20you%20do%20surveillance%20of%20a%20new%20kind%2C%20a%20surveillance%20that%20is%20not%20official%2C%20that%20is%20what%20I%20call%20societal%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20a%20deeper%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Let%E2%80%99s%20talk%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3ECJ%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20It%20is%20connected%2C%20it%20is%20connected%20of%20course%2C%20but%20not%20officially%2C%20not%20visibly%2C%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESangh%20Parivar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%