his%20is%20for%20me%20a%20clear%20indication%20that%20yes%2C%20secularism%20is%20a%20dead%20letter%20when%20there%20is%20no%20multiculturalism%20in%20places%20like%20the%20university%20system.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Let%20me%20ask%20you%20a%20question%20connected%20with%20what%20we%E2%80%99re%20talking%20about%2C%20how%20badly%20has%20the%20line%20that%20should%20separate%20religion%20and%20politics%20been%20breached%20under%20Modi%3F%20I%E2%80%99m%20referring%20to%20the%20sengol%20in%20parliament%2C%20the%20constant%20references%20to%20Hinduism%20in%20his%20speeches%2C%20and%20his%20much%20publicised%20preparation%20for%20and%20role%20in%20the%20temple%20consecration.%20Do%20you%20get%20the%20feeling%20that%20Hinduism%20is%20becoming%20the%20de%20facto%20official%20religion%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECJ%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Not%20Hinduism%2C%20Hindutva%3B%20that%20has%20become%20the%20de%20facto%20ideology%20of%20the%20country.%20You%20know%20Hindutva%20is%20not%20Hinduism%3B%20Hinduism%20cultivates%20diversity%2C%20forms%20of%20tolerance%2C%20tolerance%20which%20goes%20with%20spirituality%2C%20a%20deep%20sense%20of%20spirituality%20that%20explains%2C%20by%20the%20way%2C%20that%20Hindus%20went%20to%20Sufi%20saints%E2%80%99%20places%2C%20dargahs%2C%20in%20so%20large%20numbers.%20Hindus%20were%20open%20to%20cults%20which%20were%20not%20properly%20Hindu%2C%20because%20of%20this%20sense%20of%20spirituality.%20So%20Hindutva%20certainly%20retains%20some%20aspects%20of%20Hinduism%2C%20including%20the%20caste%20system%2C%20the%20sense%20of%20hierarchy.%20Hindutva%20is%20definitely%20elite-oriented.%20And%20it%20also%20retains%20the%20%3Cem%3Eg%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3Euru%3C%2Fem%3E-shishya%20parampara%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20Sanghis%20are%20%E2%80%98bhakts%E2%80%99%2C%20you%20know%20the%20very%20word%20%E2%80%98bhakts%E2%80%99%20is%20reference%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Eg%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3Euru%3C%2Fem%3E-shishya%20parampara%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20following%20blindly%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EGuru%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20one%20of%20the%20key%20features%20of%20this.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20Hindutva%20also%20borrows%20from%20Christianity%20and%20Islam%2C%20and%20the%20need%20for%20a%20holy%20centre%20like%20Mecca%3B%20Ayodhya%20becoming%20an%20equivalent%20to%20that%2C%20the%20need%20for%20a%20book%20like%20the%20Quran%20or%20the%20Bible%3B%20and%20the%20Bhagavad%20Gita%20is%20promoted%20as%20an%20equivalent%20for%20that.%20The%20need%20for%20big%20temples%20like%20Cathedrals%20almost%2C%20all%20this%20is%20something%20we%20saw%20as%20early%20as%20the%20making%20of%20the%20Hindutva%20movement%20in%20the%2020s%20as%20an%20emulation%2C%20an%20imitation%2C%20of%20Islam%20and%20Christianity%2C%20to%20compete%20more%20effectively%20with%20these%20two%20religions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20So%20Hindutva%20is%20not%20Hinduism%20in%20that%20sense%2C%20and%20more%20importantly%20I%20would%20add%20that%20Hindutva%20is%20an%20ethno-religious%2C%20nationalistic%C2%A0%20ideology%2C%20that%20emphasises%20the%20sacred%20character%20of%20land%2C%20the%20way%20Zionism%20does%2C%20and%20emphasises%20the%20fact%20that%20Hindus%20are%20not%20defined%20as%20believers%2C%20but%20as%20a%20people%2C%20as%20the%20descendants%20of%20the%20Vedic%20fathers.%20You%20know%20Savarkar%20says%20in%20%E2%80%98our%20vein%20runs%20the%20blood%20of%20our%20Vedic%20fathers%E2%80%99%2C%20well%20this%20is%20also%20very%20much%20what%20you%20find%20on%20the%20Zionist%20side.%20If%20you%20look%20for%20models%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20on%20the%20side%20of%20Hinduism%20that%20you%20will%20find%20them%20for%20Hindutva%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20on%20the%20European%20history%20side%2C%20on%20the%20Jewish%20history%20side%2C%20because%20these%20were%20the%20sources%20of%20inspiration.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F22153154%2Fsrinagar-2740020_1920-1024x527.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F22153154%2Fsrinagar-2740020_1920-1024x527.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F22153154%2Fsrinagar-2740020_1920-300x155.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F22153154%2Fsrinagar-2740020_1920.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-690364%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22432%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20view%20of%20Srinagar.%20Photo%3A%20A.%20Kumar%2FPixabay%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Can%20this%20Hindutva-isation%20of%20the%20country%20be%20reversed%3F%20Or%20has%20it%20gone%20so%20far%20and%20so%20deep%20that%20that%20is%20unlikely%2C%20if%20not%20impossible%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECJ%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Well%20the%20point%20of%20no-return%20has%20not%20been%20reached%20yet%2C%20I%20think%2C%20but%20if%20BJP%20lost%20power%20today%2C%20to%20return%20to%20the%20status%20quo%20will%20be%20very%20difficult.%20First%2C%20some%20laws%20will%20be%20very%20difficult%20to%20roll%20back%3B%20you%20know%2C%20can%20you%20restore%20Article%20370%3F%20Can%20you%20abolish%20the%20new%20CAA%3F%20Can%20you%20make%20conversions%20and%20inter-religious%20marriages%20easier%20again%3F%20No%2C%20the%20legitimacy%20of%20such%20moves%20will%20be%20contested%20in%20the%20street%2C%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20back%20to%20my%20deeper%20state%20argumen