s%20talk%20Professor%20Jaffrelot%2C%20a%20little%20about%20Modi%20the%20person%3B%20he%E2%80%99s%20an%20incomparable%20orator%2C%20he%20has%20indefatigable%20energy%2C%20and%20he%E2%80%99s%20hugely%20popular.%20How%20does%20his%20personality%20compare%20to%20other%20long%20serving%20Prime%20Ministers%20like%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20and%20Indira%20Gandhi%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECJ%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Well%20Nehru%20was%20very%20different%2C%20but%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20personality%20has%20clear%20affinities%20with%20Mrs%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%3B%20both%20are%20authoritarian%20personalities%2C%20you%20know%20a%20psychological%20type%20that%20has%20been%20studied%20scientifically%20by%20scholars%20since%20the%201950s.%20Authoritarian%20personalities%20do%20not%20trust%20more%20than%20a%20handful%20of%20people%2C%20because%20they%20are%20fundamentally%20insecure%2C%20and%20they%20believe%20that%20power%20is%20an%20end%20in%20itself.%20But%20again%20as%20I%E2%80%99ve%20said%20before%2C%20there%20is%20a%20big%20difference%20between%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20and%20Narendra%20Modi%3B%20for%20Modi%20the%20ultimate%20goal%20is%20the%20transformation%20of%20India%20into%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHindu%20Rashtra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20did%20not%20have%20such%20a%20long-term%20objective.%20You%20know%20the%20emergency%2C%20as%20we%20show%20in%20our%20book%20with%20Pratinav%20Anil%2C%20was%20a%20damage%20control%20exercise%2C%20and%20it%20could%20last%20only%20for%2022%20months%20for%20that%20very%20reason.%20Here%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20very%20different%20game%2C%20this%20personality%20has%20an%20ideology%20and%20an%20ultimate%20goal%20for%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Let%20me%20ask%20you%20a%20little%20about%20Nehru%2C%20Modi%20is%20constantly%20targeting%20and%20belittling%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%3B%20do%20you%20suspect%20he%20has%20a%20complex%20about%20him%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECJ%