20Modi%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20like%20critics%2C%20whether%20they%E2%80%99re%20journalists%20or%20whether%20they%E2%80%99re%20other%20politicians.%20He%20uses%20terror%20and%20money%20laundering%20laws%20against%20them%2C%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20hold%20press%20conferences%2C%20he%20only%20gives%20interviews%20to%20Anchors%20who%20will%20never%20challenge%20him.%20What%20does%20this%20tell%20us%20about%20his%20political%20personality%3F%20Does%20it%2C%20as%20I%20get%20the%20feeling%2C%20hint%20at%20insecurity%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECJ%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Yes%2C%20authoritarian%20personalities%20are%20insecure%20personalities.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20interact%20with%20others%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20argue.%20They%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20contradicted%20because%20they%20lose%20their%20temper%20usually%2C%20when%20contradicted.%20Yes%2C%20but%20I%20would%20say%20something%20else.%20I%20would%20say%20that%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Modi%2C%20why%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20accept%20interactions%2C%20press%20conferences%2C%20because%20his%20discourse%20describes%20an%20India%20that%20does%20not%20exist.%20So%20when%20you%20live%20in%20this%20fantasy%2C%20when%20you%20have%20painted%20such%20a%20rosy%20picture%2C%20any%20way%20questioning%20this%20myth%20opens%20a%20kind%20of%20vacuum.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20know%20the%20economy%20is%20not%20doing%20well%2C%20the%20country%20is%20terribly%20vulnerable%20vis-a-vis%20China%3B%20you%20look%20the%20other%20way%20when%20this%20question%20is%20mentioned%2C%20how%20do%20you%20admit%20that%20China%20is%20encroaching%20on%20your%20territory%20and%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20react%3F%20So%20you%20better%20not%20have%20a%20question%20on%20that%20either.%20So%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20he%20does%20with%20his%20%E2%80%98Mann%20Ki%20Baat%E2%80%99%20every%20month%2C%20painting%20a%20rosy%20picture%2C%20an%20ideal%20picture%2C%20and