n%20India%2C%20to%20some%20extent%2C%20Islamists%20have%20helped%20the%20RSS%20to%20disseminate%20its%20views%2C%20because%20by%20instigating%20terrorist%20attacks%20they%20gave%20a%20good%20argument%2C%20%E2%80%98saying%20that%20yes%2C%20you%20are%20vulnerable%2C%20yes%20you%20need%20to%20develop%20a%20new%20identity%E2%80%99.%20But%20the%20rise%20of%20Hindutva%20predates%20these%20attacks%2C%20you%20know.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20early%20as%20the%201980s%20we%20saw%20the%20RSS%2C%20after%20penetrating%20Society%20for%20so%20many%20decades%2C%20embarking%20on%20a%20key%20campaign%3B%20you%20know%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ERam%20Janmabhoomi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20movement%20that%20was%20started%20after%20the%20Janta%20party%20left%20the%20scene%2C%20after%20RSS%20realised%20that%20there%20was%20no%20way%20Jang%20Sangh%2C%20now%20BJP%2C%20could%20be%20part%20of%20a%20coalition%3B%20a%20Hindu%20vote%20bank%20had%20to%20be%20created%2C%20a%20majoritarian%20Hindu%20vote%20bank%20had%20to%20be%20created.%20And%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ERam%20Janmabhoomi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20movement%20was%20precisely%20dedicated%20to%20this%20task.%20So%20the%20mobilisation%20played%20on%20emotions%2C%20transforming%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20Hindu%20majority.%20The%20main%20emotion%20was%20anger%3B%20you%20know%20you%20have%20fear%20and%20anger%2C%20these%20are%20the%20two%20emotions%20the%20national%20populist%20play%20with.%20Anger%20because%20God%20was%20behind%20bars%2C%20you%20know%20remember%20God%20must%20be%20liberated%2C%20that%20was%20the%20motto.%20And%20I%20think%20this%20mobilisation%20of%20course%20again%20momentum%2C%20peaked%20after%2010%20years%20with%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%2C%20riots%20after%20riots%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eyatras%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20after%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eyatras%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20you%20know%20what%20we%20see%20today%20is%20the%20result%20of%20a%20long%20proc