-bjps-1st-list-of-195-candidates-for-lok-sabha-polls-5163186%5C%22%3Eclear%20message%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it's%20prepared%20for%20the%20battle%20and%20confident%20of%20securing%20a%20third%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20list%20balances%20demographic%20considerations%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20refrained%20from%20granting%20tickets%20to%20several%20MPs%2C%20signalling%20a%20change%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20neutralise%20local-level%20anti-incumbency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20BJP's%20first%20list%20of%20184%20candidates%20was%20unveiled%20on%20March%2021.%20Back%20then%2C%20the%20list%20appeared%2011%20days%20after%20the%20announcement%20of%20polls%20on%20March%2010.%20This%20time%2C%20the%20list%20has%20arrived%20before%20the%20poll%20dates%20have%20been%20disclosed%2C%20aligning%20with%20the%20strategy%20deployed%20in%20state%20elections%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Slew%20Of%20New%20Players%20In%20UP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20195%20seats%20announced%2C%20a%20majority%20-%2051%20-%20seats%2C%20are%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-2024-lok-sabha-elections-list-ravi-kishan-hottest-seat-after-kashi-ravi-kishan-after-bjp-fields-him-from-ups-gorakhpur-5166536%5C%22%3EUttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%20(26%25).%20This%20is%20where%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20senses%20the%20maximum%20potential%20for%20gains%2C%20having%20secured%2064%20of%20the%2080%20seats%20in%202019.%20It%20has%20set%20an%20internal%20target%20of%2080%2F80%20due%20to%20the%20positive%20fervour%20generated%20post%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%20195%20seats%20announced%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20won%20152%20in%202019%20and%20lost%2043.%20Among%20the%20152%20who%20won%2C%20the%20party%20has%20replaced%2044%20MPs%20(29%25).%20Of%20the%2043%20candidates%20who%20lost%20in%202019%2C%20it%20has%20replaced%2037.%20In%20total%2C%20there%20are%20114%20old%20faces%20(58%25)%20and%2081%20new%20faces%20(42%25).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20won%20303%20seats%20in%202019%2C%20the%20current%20number%20of%20sitting%20MPs%20is%20290%20due%20to%20the%20demise%20of%20some%20MPs%2C%20losses%20in%20by-polls%2C%20and%20resignations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%2044%20out%20of%20the%2051%20names%20announced%20are%20sitting%20MPs.%20That%20share%20is%2013%20out%20of%2024%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-first-list-lok-sabha-election-2024-in-madhya-pradesh-shivraj-chouhan-gets-ticket-pragya-thakur-does-not-5165057%5C%22%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2010%20out%20of%2015%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20and%20three%20out%20of%20four%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFighting%20Anti-Incumbency%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20dropped%2037%25%20of%20its%20sitting%20MPs.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20marginal%20drop%20this%20time%20though.%20This%20has%20been%20the%20BJP's%20common%20theme%20in%20the%20Modi-Shah%20era%2C%20right%20from%20their%20days%20at%20the%20helm%20in%20Gujarat.%20The%20duo%20likes%20to%20churn%20MPs%20to%20neutralise%20anti-incumbency%20sentiments%20and%20provide%20opportunities%20to%20new%20leaders.%20This%20helps%20broaden%20the%20party's%20base%20and%20reduce%20dependency%20on%20local%20leadership%20in%20an%20era%20when%20elections%20are%20becoming%20increasingly%20presidential%20in%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%2052%25%20of%20the%20candidates%20announced%20belong%20to%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBC)%2C%20or%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SC)%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(ST)%20communities.%20This%20strengthens%20the%20BJP's%20claim%20of%20giving%20the%20highest%20representation%20to%20the%20backward%2C%20Dalit%2C%20and%20Adivasi%20communities.%20One%20ticket%20has%20also%20been%20given%20to%20a%20Muslim%20candidate%20in%20Kerala.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20representation%20of%20women%20is%20at%2014%20per%20cent%2C%20much%20lower%20than%20the%20promised%2033%25%20reservation.%20However%2C%20this%20is%20likely%20to%20increase%20in%20subsequent%20lists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20Decision%20Yet%20On%20Maharashtra%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Odisha%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETickets%20have%20not%20been%20announced%20for%20Maharashtra%20and%20Bihar%2C%20where%20alliance%20seat-sharing%20talks%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20finalised.%20In%20both%20places%2C%20there%20is%20an%20abundance%20of%20contenders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeats%20have%20also%20not%20been%20announced%20for%20Odisha%2C%20where%20there%20is%20speculation%20about%20the%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)%C2%A0%20joining%20the%20NDA%20if%20a%20Bharat%20Ratna%20is%20awarded%20to%20Biju%20Patnaik%2C%20whose%20birth%20anniversary%20is%20on%20March%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Maharashtra%2C%20seats%20have%20to%20be%20divided%20among%20three%20parties%20-%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(SHS)%2C%20and%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20-%20and%20in%20Bihar%2C%20six%20parties%20have%20to%20be%20accommodated%20-%20the%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(LJP)%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20(JD-U)%2C%20the%20Hindustani%20Awam%20Morcha%20(HAM)%2C%20the%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Samta%20Party%20(RLSP)%2C%20and%20the%20Vikassheel%20Insaan%20Party%20(VIP).%20Representatives%20from%20the%20LJP%20and%20the%20RLSP%20were%20conspicuously%20absent%20from%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20recent%20rally%20in%20Aurangabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETwo-Term%20MPs%20Replaced%20In%20Delhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Delhi%2C%20out%20of%20the%20five%20seats%2C%20four%20sitting%20MPs%20have%20been%20replaced.%20Three%20out%20of%20the%20four%20were%20two-term%20MPs.%20Manoj%20Tiwari%2C%20who%20retains%20his%20seat%2C%20is%20also%20a%20two-term%20MP.%20In%202019%2C%20out%20of%20the%2099%20sitting%20MPs%20who%20were%20dropped%2C%2044%20of%20them