.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20National%20Commission%20for%20Protection%20of%20Child%20Rights%20(NCPCR)%20has%20urged%20the%20government%20to%20take%20action%20against%20the%20Ullu%20App%20for%20disseminating%20obscene%20material%20to%20minors.%20The%20app%20targets%20school%20children%20with%20explicit%20content%2C%20violating%20the%20POCSO%20Act%20and%20lacking%20age%20verification%20systems.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fnpcr-complains-to-it-ministry-against-ullu-app-says-distributing-obscene-objectionable-content%2Farticleshow%2F108194883.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIf%20Any%20Word%20Hurt%20PM...%26quot%3B%3A%20Pragya%20Thakur%20After%20BJP%20Denies%20Her%20Poll%20Pass%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20BJP%20replaced%20Pragya%20Singh%20Thakur%20as%20its%20candidate%20from%20Bhopal%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20the%20firebrand%20leader%20has%20said%20she%20had%20apologised%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20soon%20after%20her%20controversial%20remark%20about%20Nathuram%20Godse%20in%202019.%20She%20added%20that%20she%20has%20never%20asked%20for%20a%20ticket%20to%20contest%20polls%20and%20would%20do%20whatever%20the%20party%20asks%20here%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Thakur%2C%20an%20accused%20in%20the%202008%20Malegaon%20blast%20case%2C%20was%20elected%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20from%20Bhopal%20in%20the%202019%20general%20election.%20Soon%20after%2C%20her%20remark%20describing%20Mahatma%20Gandhi's%20killer%20Nathuram%20Godse%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bpatriot%26quot%3B%20sparked%20a%20huge%20row.%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20had%20then%20said%20the%20statements%20were%20%26quot%3Bwrong%20for%20the%20society%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BShe%20has%20apologised%2C%20but%20I%20will%20never%20forgive%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%