ration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty.%20Photo%3A%20Intifada%20P.%20Basheer%20and%20Azam%20Abbas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20examination%20for%20411%20posts%20of%20RO%20and%20ARO%20was%20conducted%20by%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20on%20February%2011.%20Not%20just%20the%20recruitment%20exams%20for%20government%20jobs%2C%20even%20board%20exams%20held%20in%20the%20state%20are%20now%20facing%20allegations%20of%20paper%20leak.%20Police%20in%20Agra%20have%20arrested%20three%20persons%2C%20including%20the%20principal%20of%20an%20inter-college%2C%20for%20allegedly%20leaking%20biology%20and%20maths%20question%20papers%20of%20the%20state%20secondary%20board%20education%20examination%20held%20on%20February%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2024%2C%20after%20massive%20protests%20by%20aspirants%20in%20several%20cities%2C%20the%20government%20cancelled%20the%20police%20constable%20recruitment%20examination%20but%20only%20initiated%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20RO%20and%20ARO%20examination%20despite%20similar%20charges.%20The%20RO%20and%20ARO%20aspirants%20continued%20to%20protest%20and%20on%20March%202%2C%202024%2C%20Adityanath%20announced%20that%20the%20February%2011%20examination%20was%20cancelled.%20He%20instructed%20the%20UPPSC%20to%20hold%20the%20exams%20again%20within%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThose%20who%20play%20with%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20examination%20will%20not%20be%20spared%20under%20any%20circumstances.%C2%A0The%20culprits%20will%20be%20given%C2%A0such%20a%C2%A0punishment%C2%A0that%C2%A0will%20set%20an%20example%2C%E2%80%9D%20Adityanath%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuestion%20of%20lakhs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2010%20lakh%20aspirants%20had%20appeared%20for%20the%20RO%20and%20ARO%20examination%20while%20more%20than%2048%20lakh%C2%A0aspirants%C2%A0were%20vying%20for%20a%20mere%2067%2C000%C2%A0police%C2%A0constable%C2%A0jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20302px)%2085vw%2C%20302px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F04091502%2FGHqrVAfXwAAAlYs-767x1024.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22302%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F04091502%2FGHqrVAfXwAAAlYs-767x1024.jpeg%20767w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F04091502%2FGHqrVAfXwAAAlYs-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F04091502%2FGHqrVAfXwAAAlYs.jpeg%20899w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-699981%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22403%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20of%20Congress%20holds%20up%20a%20poster%20calling%20for%20justice%20for%20RO%20and%20ARO%20position%20examinees%20during%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40INCUttarPradesh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20of%20paper%20leak%20and%20corruption%20in%20these%20examinations%20provided%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20fodder%20to%20question%20the%20record%20of%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20conducting%20free%20and%20fair%20exams%20and%20ensuring%20a%20smooth%20process%20for%20providing%20jobs%20to%20the%20youth%20against%20rampant%20unemployment%20and%20underemployment.%20%C2%A0Unemployment%20has%20emerged%20as%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20issues%20that%20the%20Opposition%20parties%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20Congress%2C%20are%20using%20to%20plug%20holes%20into%20the%20claims%20of%20prosperity%20and%20development%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20alleged%20paper%20leak%20in%20the%20board%20examinations%20have%20further%20raised%20serious%20questions%20on%20the%20fairness%20of%20examinations%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%20According%20to%20an%20FIR%20lodged%20in%20Fatehpur%20Sikri%20police%20station%20in%20Agra%2C%20on%20February%2029%2C%20at%20around%203%3A11%20pm%2C%20when%20the%20board%20examinations%20were%20going%20on%2C%20photos%20of%20the%20maths%20and%20biology%20question%20papers%20were%20shared%20on%20a%20Whatsapp%20group%20called%20%E2%80%98All%20Principals%20Agra%E2%80%99%20by%20a%20phone%20number%20linked%20to%20one%20Vinay%20Chaudhary%2C%20a%20computer%20operator%20Athar%20Singh%20Inter-College%20in%20Fatehpur%20Sikri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20police%20complaint%2C%20Dinesh%20Kumar%2C%20the%20district%20inspector%20of%20Schools%2C%20accused%20four%20identified%20persons%2C%20Chaudhary%2C%20his%20father%20Rajendra%20Singh%20(principal%20of%20Athar%20Singh%20Inter%20College)%2C%20Gambhir%20Singh%20(additional%20centre%20administrator%20at%20GSK%20Inter%20College)%20and%20Gajendra%20Singh%20(static%20magistrate%20and%20veterinary%20officer)%20for%20the%20paper%20leak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20invoked%20sections%203%20and%204%20of%20the%20UP%20Public%20Examination%C2%A0(Prevention%C2%A0of%C2%A0Unfair%C2%A0Means)%C2%A0Act%201998%C2%A0and%20section%2072%20of%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Act%20against%20the%20accused.%20Chaudhary%2C%20Rajendra%20Singh%20and%20Gambhir%20Singh%20have%20been%20arrested%2C%20said%20police.%20The%20UP%20Intermediate%20Education%20Department%2C%20had%2C%20however%20clarified%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20examination%20that%20the%20alleged%20leak%20of%20the%20paper%20was%20a%20stray%20act%20carried%20out%20by%20an%20individual%2C%20Chaudhary%2C%20to%20help%20a%20student%20to%20cheat.%20The%20overall%20sanctity%20of%20the%20examination%20was%20not%20affected%2C%20claimed%20Dibyakant%20Shukla%2C%20secretary%20of%20the%20UP%20Madhyamik%20Shiksha%20Parishad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20argued%20that%20the%20examination%20was%20scheduled%20from%202%20pm%20to%205%3A15%20pm%20but%20the%20papers%20were%20leaked%20on%20the%20WhatsApp%20group%20at%20around%203%3A10%20pm.%20By%20this%20time%2C%20the%20exam%20had%20already%20been%20conducted%20for%20more%20than%20an%20hour%2C%20said%20Shukla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Flakh-aspirants-jobs-exams-constable-recruitment%5C%22%3E48%20Lakh%20Aspirants%20For%2067%2C000%20Jobs%3A%20How%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Conducted%20the%20Constable%20Recruitment%20Exam%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETwo%20die%20by%20suicide%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20streak%20of%20paper%20leaks%20and%20disruption%20of%20the%20normal%20exam%20schedule%20has%20been%20a%20great%20cause%20of%20stress%20for%20lakhs%20of%20aspirants%20who%20hope%20to%20secure%20government%20jobs.%20In%20Firozabad%2C%20a%2022-year-old%20woman%20died%20by%20suicide%20by%20hanging%20herself.%20A%20note%20left%20behind%20by%20her%20said%20that%20she%20was%20depressed%20over%20not%20finding%20a%20job%20and%20the%20recent%20paper%20leaks%2C%20said%20police%20on%20March%202.%20Last%20week%2C%20a%2024-year-old%20man%20died%20in%20similar%20circumstances%20in%20Kannauj%20as%20he%20was%20aggrieved%20over%20not%20finding%20a%20job%20despite%20appearing%20in%20several%20exams%2C%20including%20the%20police%20constable%20recruitment%20exam%2C%20his%20family%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamajwadi%20Party%20president%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20said%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20RO%20and%20ARO%20examinations%20shows%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20the%20BJP%20first%20tries%20every%20possible%20way%20to%20hide%20its%20misdeeds%20but%20when%20there%20is%20public%20pressure%2C%20it%20retreats%20due%20to%20the%20fear%20of%20electoral%20defeat.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20victory%20of%20the%20youth%20and%20another%20sure%20message%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20defeat%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%20The%20paper%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20defeat%20has%20been%20leaked.%20Remove%20BJP%2C%20get%20a%20job!%E2%80%9D%20Yadav%20said%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20also%20took%20to%20the%20social%20media%20site%20to%20ask%20why%20almost%20every%20paper%E2%80%94from%20jobs%20to%20board%20exams%E2%80%94were%20being%20leaked%20in%20UP.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20save%20the%20examination%20mafia%20and%20the%20corrupt%20people%20sitting%20in%20the%20government%2C%20BJP%20is%20also%20making%20hollow%20the%20foundation%20of%20crores%20of%20children%20and%20youth%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vadra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20police%20probe%20the%20board%20exam%20paper%20leak%20in%20Agra%20and%20the%20RO%20and%20ARO%20examinations%2C%20it%20is%20still%20arresting%20people%20who%20allegedly%20leaked%20the%20police%20constable%20exam%20question%20paper%20on%20February%2017%20and%2018.%20Kapil%20Tomar%2C%20an%20accused%2C%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20UP%20Special%20Task%20Force%20for%20allegedly%20trying%20to%20help%20someone%20cheat%20in%20the%20exam%20through%20a%20Bluetooth%20device%20in%20Ghaziabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709524018000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F04091112%2FUntitled-design-4.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Futtar-pradesh-exams-cancellations-protests%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Over%2010%20lakh%20aspirants%20had%20appeared%20for%20the%20RO%20and%20ARO%20examinations%20%E2%80%93%20now%20cancelled%20%E2%80%93%20while%20more%20than%2048%20lakh%C2%A0aspirants%C2%A0were%20vying%20for%20a%20mere%2067%2C000%C2%A0police%C2%A0constable%C2%A0jobs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Futtar-pradesh-exams-cancellations-protests%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22State%20of%20emergency%20in%20Haiti%20as%20gang%20leader%20seeks%20to%20oust%20prime%20minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709523540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F03%2F768x432%2Fskynews-haiti-port-au-prince_6477824.jpg%3F20240304035039%22%2C%22originID%2