rame%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FJzktUiRDcp0%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%9F%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%A7%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%88%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%A6%20%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%87%E0%A4%B5%20%7C%20The%20Wire%20Live%20%7C%20Patna%20%7C%20Gandhi%20Maidan%20%7C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20%7C%20RJD%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJobs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20training%20his%20guns%20on%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20Tejashwi%20appeared%20to%20keep%20the%20jobs%20question%20front%20and%20centre%20and%20tried%20to%20present%20himself%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98store%20house%E2%80%99%20of%20employment.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20the%20same%20Gandhi%20Maidan%20in%20which%20I%20made%20a%20reluctant%20CM%20%5Ba%20jab%20at%20Nitish%20Kumar%20who%20left%20the%20alliance%20recently%5D%20distribute%20over%20two%20lakh%20appointment%20letters.%20Do%20you%20remember%20it%20or%20not%3F%E2%80%9D%20Tejashwi%20asked.%20People%20responded%20with%20rousing%20cries%20of%20%E2%80%98Tejashwi%20%3Cem%3Ezindabad%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmployment%20has%20been%20in%20the%20centre%20of%20Tejashwi%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20ever%20since%20the%202020%20elections.%20Behind%20his%20description%20of%20Modi%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfactory%20of%20lies%E2%80%9D%20was%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20had%20reneged%20on%20his%20promise%20to%20give%20two%20crores%20of%20jobs%20annually%20apart%20from%20raising%20the%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20for%20agricultural%20products%20up%20to%2050%25%20and%20doubling%20farmers%E2%80%99%20income%20by%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20Modi%20ji%20who%20failed%20on%20several%20of%20his%20guarantees%20in%20the%20past%20is%20talking%20about%20%E2%80%98Modi%20%3Cem%3Eki%3C%2Fem%3E%20guarantee%E2%80%99.%20What%20guarantee%20he%20is%20talking%20about%3F%E2%80%9D%20Tejashwi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWill%20he%20%5BModi%5D%20guarantee%20the%20stay%20of%20my%20uncle%20%5BTejashwi%20calls%20Nitish%20%E2%80%98uncle%E2%80%99%5D%20with%20him%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Tejashwi%20has%20tried%20to%20match%20the%20gift%20of%20rhetoric%20that%20his%20father%20had%2C%20it%20is%20too%20early%20to%20say%20if%20he%20will%20prove%20to%20have%20Lalu%E2%80%99s%20exact%20power%20to%20mesmerise%20the%20masses%20and%20take%20on%20political%20opponents%20in%20the%20parliament%20and%20on%20the%20streets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frjds-jan-vishwas-patna-rally-turns-into-a-big-india-push-first-in-hindi-belt-in-2024%5C%22%3ERJD%E2%80%99s%20Jan%20Vishwas%20Patna%20Rally%20Turns%20Into%20a%20Big%20INDIA%20Push%2C%20First%20in%20Hindi%20Belt%20in%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESoft%20on%20Nitish%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20comparison%20to%20his%20barbs%20against%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Tejashwi%20was%20mild%20on%20Nitish.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20uncle%20deserted%20us.%20But%20I%20have%20no%20issue%3B%20I%20respected%20him%3B%20I%20will%20keep%20on%20respecting%20him.%20He%20is%20an%20old%20man.%20I%20have%20all%20regards%20for%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20point%2C%20though%2C%20he%20was%20unsparing.%20%E2%80%9CJust%20remember%20who%20talked%20about%20jobs%20and%20employment%20first.%20It%20was%20I%20who%20promised%20to%20give%2010%20lakh%20jobs%20during%20my%202020%20election%20campaigns.%20But%2C%20Nitish%20screamed%20at%20me%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%98Where%20will%20we%20get%20the%20money%20from%3F%20Will%20I%20bring%20it%20from%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20house%3F%20This%20is%20impossible%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETejashwi%2C%20who%20was%20driven%20to%20the%20opposit