Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EIt's%20more%20about%20the%20home%20ground%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20Wolf%20Warrior%20diplomat's%20specific%20behaviors%20and%20level%20of%20aggression%20are%20unlikely%20to%20come%20at%20the%20direct%20instruction%20of%20their%20superiors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%2C%20it%20stems%20from%20an%20expectation%20for%20diplomats%20to%20protect%20Beijing's%20image%20fiercely%2C%20said%20Stanley%20Rosen%2C%20professor%20of%20political%20science%20and%20international%20relations%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Southern%20California's%20US-China%20Institute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnybody%20who's%20a%20diplomat%20for%20China%20who%20wants%20to%20be%20promoted%20cannot%20take%20the%20soft%20line%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosen%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20to%20be%20defending%20China%20at%20all%20times.%20So%20you'll%20get%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20trouble%20and%20not%20get%20promoted%20if%20you%20seem%20to%20be%20too%20sympathetic%20to%20the%20foreigners.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20a%20diplomat%20who%20gets%20too%20aggressive%20might%20be%20asked%20to%20tone%20it%20down%2C%20but%20would%20rarely%20be%20sacked%20or%20face%20severe%20consequences%2C%20Rosen%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerceptions%20at%20home%20are%20key%20to%20China's%20diplomatic%20approach%2C%20Rosen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNumber%20one%2C%20China's%20most%20concerned%20with%20its%20own%20domestic%20population%2C%20and%20they're%20playing%20to%20that%20population%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpelosi-taiwan-visit-prompts-anti-american-vitriol-weibo-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina's%20jingoistic%20nationalist%20crowd%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20extremely%20active%20on%20social%20media%2C%20and%20sometimes%20goes%20so%20far%20as%20to%20demand%20Beijing%20declares%20war%20over%20diplomatic%20slights.%20Zhao%20had%20been%20one%20of%20its%20most%20popular%20