a%2C%20and%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20coming%20in%20lower%20on%20China's%20priorities%20is%20the%20Western%20public%2C%20Rosen%20said%2C%20though%20it%20has%20a%20stake%20in%20opinions%20from%20the%20Western%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20they%20care%20is%20they%20want%20the%20technology%2C%20they%20want%20the%20investment%2C%20they%20want%20to%20trade%2C%20they%20want%20to%20sell%20their%20goods%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20cost%20of%20tongue-lashing%20and%20knocking%20heads%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20true%20that%20China%20has%20shown%20signs%20of%20dialing%20back%20its%20rhetoric%2C%20that's%20more%20of%20a%20recalibration%20than%20an%20overhaul%2C%20the%20experts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPan%20Chengxin%2C%20who%20teaches%20international%20relations%20at%20Deakin%20University%20in%20Australia%2C%20said%20Beijing%20started%20using%20its%20Wolf%20Warrior%20style%20in%20light%20of%20a%20more%20hostile%20global%20environment%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-china-relationship-pushed-to-brink-trump-xi-jinping-coronavirus-2020-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eformer%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20loudly%20confrontational%20policies%20toward%20China%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20takes%20two%20to%20tango%20in%20international%20relations%2C%26quot%3B%20Pan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20mounting%20challenges%20for%20the%20West%2C%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-israel-trying-to-achieve-in-gaza-bombing-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewars%20in%20Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Ukraine%2C%20mean%20confrontation%20with%20China%20is%20taking%20more%20of%20a%20backseat%2C%20said%20Dylan%20Loh%2C%20who%20teaches%20Chinese%20foreign%20policy%20and%20international%20relations%20at%20the%20Nanyang%20Technological%20University%20of%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Chinese%20leader%20Xi%20Jinping%20is%20likely%20refocusing%20on%20rescuing%20a%20struggling%20domestic%20economy%20and%20fixing%20internal%20issues%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20China%20and%20the%20US%20know%20that%20it%20would%20not%20be%20possible%20to%20get%20along%20happily%20all%20the%20time%2C%20but%20the%20focus%20will%20shift%20toward%20managing%20conflict%20and%20distrust%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223401%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Biden%20and%20Xi%20met%20in%20person%20at%20the%20APEC%202023%20summit%2C%20a%20positive%20note%20in%20US-China%20relations%20as%20both%20countries%20continually%20clashed%20%20in%20recent%20years.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e1805590413ab8e1d8172a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBiden%20and%20Xi%20met%20in%20person%20at%20the%20APEC%202023%20summit%2C%20a%20positive%20note%20in%20US-China%20relations%20as%20both%20countries%20continually%20clashed%20in%20recent%20years.%3Cp%3EBRENDAN%20SMIALOWSKI%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20is%20also%20aware%20that%20the%20shock%20value%20of%20Wolf%20Warrior%20diplomacy%20brings%20diminishing%20returns.%20Countries%20would%20simply%20get%20used%20to%20its%20aggression.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20limits%20of%20wolf%20warrior%20diplomacy%20are%20apparent%2C%26quot%3B%20Loh%20said.%20%26quot%3BNo%20one%20country%2C%20not%20China%20or%20even%20the%20US%2C%20can%20completely%20bully%20or%20shout%20their%20way%20through%20every%20single%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Beijing%20wants%20the%20same%20effect%2C%20they%20will%20have%20to%20escalate%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chong%20of%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore.%20%26quot%3BThat%20brings%20with%20it%20additional%20risks%2C%20situations%20getting%20out%20of%20control.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20Wolf%20Warrior%20will%20be%20back%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20Wolf%20Warrior%20diplomacy%20will%20return%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20issue%20at%20hand%2C%20said%20Loh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20of%20the%20matter%20is%20that%20assertive%20diplomacy%20was%20present%20before%20even%20the%20term%20was%20coined%2C%20but%20it%20was%20certainly%20accelerated%20by%20Xi%20Jinping%2C%26quot%3B%20Loh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223097%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Former%20Chinese%20Foreign%20Minister%20Qin%20Gang%20shakes%20hands%20with%20US%20State%20Secretary%20Antony%20Blinken%20in%20June%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e184226080194819fb7293%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222065%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFormer%20Chinese%20Foreign%20Minister%20Qin%20Gang%2C%20known%20for%20building%20up%20Wolf%20Warrior%20diplomacy%2C%20was%20fired%20from%20his%20post%20and%20disappeared%20from%20the%20public%20eye%20amid%20corruption%20and%20an%20affair%20scandal.%20HIs%20ejection%20prompted%20some%20suspicion%20that%20Wolf%20Warrior%20diplomacy%20was%20no%20longer%20China's%20strategy.%3Cp%3ELEAH%20MILLIS%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20why%20did%20Liu%20tell%20reporters%20and%20academics%20in%20New%20York%20that%20Wolf%20Warrior%20diplomacy%20would%20never%20return%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20one%2C%20Rosen%20said%2C%20the%20West%20coined%20the%20term%2C%20and%20Beijing%20doesn't%20use%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20name%20now%20carries%20so%20many%20negative%20connotations%20that%20China%20is%20likely%20pushing%20harder%20for%20the%20world%20to%20drop%20the%20concept%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20would%20just%20be%20the%20name%20that%20China%20tries%20to%20scrub%20away%2C%20not%20the%20behavior%20that%20created%20the%20Wolf%20Warrior%20reputation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20the%20Chinese%20government%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhen%20something%20develops%20what%20I%20might%20call%20a%20bad%20smell%2C%