%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fgaza-truce-talks-us-puts-pressure-on-hamas-to-clinch-ceasefire-deal-on-table-13086402%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20path%20to%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza%20is%20%26quot%3Bstraightforward%20and%20there's%20a%20deal%20on%20the%20table%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20senior%20US%20official%20has%20said%2C%20as%20mediators%20return%20to%20Egypt%20hoping%20to%20reach%20an%20agreement%20before%20Ramadan%20begins%20in%20a%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fgaza-truce-talks-us-puts-pressure-on-hamas-to-clinch-ceasefire-deal-on-table-13086402%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fgaza-truce-talks-us-puts-pressure-on-hamas-to-clinch-ceasefire-deal-on-table-13086402%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fgaza-truce-talks-us-puts-pressure-on-hamas-to-clinch-ceasefire-deal-on-table-13086402%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2210-Day%20Yatra%20and%20a%20Mega%20Rally%3A%20Tejashwi%20Attempts%20to%20Go%20Beyond%20Muslim-Yadav%20Formula%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03192044%2FGHP5gulWQAIOIL_.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPatna%20(Bihar)%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Patna%E2%80%99s%20Gandhi%20Maidan%2C%20a%20barometer%20to%20measure%20the%20political%20clout%2C%20on%20Sunday%20witnessed%20a%20substantial%20crowd%20in%20a%20mega%20rally%20organised%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emahagathbandhan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%20the%20grand%20alliance%20which%20consists%20of%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%2C%20Congress%2C%20CPI-ML%20(Liberation)%20and%20other%20left%20parties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20crowd%20shouted%20and%20clapped%20at%20every%20sentence%20uttered%20by%20the%20leader%20of%20opposition%20and%20former%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Tejashwi%20Yadav.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYadav%20took%20credit%20for%20providing%20employment%20to%20the%20youth%20during%20his%20short%20tenure%20as%20deputy%20chief%20and%20said%20that%20he%20will%20continue%20to%20raise%20the%20issue%20of%20unemployment%20among%20youths.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20BJP%20is%20his%20core%20political%20rival.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERJD%20supremo%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%2C%20Rabri%20Devi%2C%20Misa%20Bharti%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20CPI(M)%20leader%20Sitaram%20Yechury%2C%20CPI-ML%20(Liberation)%20leader%20Dipankar%20Bhattacharya%20and%20other%20leaders%20were%20present%20in%20the%20rally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20rally%20was%20the%20culmination%20of%2010-day%20long%20Jan%20Vishwas%20Yatra%20of%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20which%20started%20on%20February%2020%2C%20weeks%20after%20Nitish%20Kumar%20ditched%20the%20mahagathbandhan%20and%20went%20back%20to%20NDA%20(National%20Democratic%20Alliance).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20yatra%20covered%20a%20distance%20of%203%2C500%20kilometres%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewitnessing%20an%20unexpectedly%20large%20crowd.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20yatra%2C%20Tejashwi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20focused%20on%20employment%20and%20said%20that%20RJD%20is%20the%20party%20for%20all.%20He%20even%20moved%20beyond%20RJD%E2%80%99s%20trademark%20slogan%20of%20social%20justice%20and%20talked%20about%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esamajik%20nyay%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(social%20justice)%20along%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Earthik%20nyay%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(economic%20justice).%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEconomic%20development%20along%20with%20social%20justice%20slogan%20was%20coined%20by%20Nitish%20Kumar%20soon%20after%20he%20became%20chief%20minister%20in%202005.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDecoding%20the%20crowd%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERJD%20sources%20said%20that%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20yatra%20attracted%20a%20huge%20crowd%2C%20it%20was%20taken%20through%20those%20areas%20that%20are%20considered%20as%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20strongholds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdditionally%2C%20local%20RJD%20MLAs%20were%20instructed%20to%20bring%20people%20from%20their%20areas%20on%20the%20yatra%20route.%20The%20other%20alliance%20partners%20of%20the%20mahagathbandhan%2C%20like%20CPI-ML%20workers%2C%20were%20also%20tasked%20to%20gather%20the%20crowd.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20journalists%20who%20covered%20Tejashwi%E2%80%99s%20yatra%20said%20that%20the%20crowd%20primarily%20consisted%20of%20RJD%E2%80%99s%20core%20supporters%20%E2%80%93%20Yadavs%20and%20Muslims.%20However%2C%20people%20from%20other%20castes%20also%20participated%20in%20the%20yatra%2C%20but%20their%20number%20was%20relatively%20less.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20journalist%20who%20covered%20the%20yatra%20in%20Nalanda%20said%20that%20there%20were%20mostly%20youngsters%20in%20the%20rally%2C%20and%20they%20were%20mostly%20from%20Yadav%20and%20Muslim%20communities.%20Other%20castes%20also%20joined%20the%20rally%20but%20in%20lesser%20numbers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYouths%20were%20jubilant%20and%20it%20seems%20they%20are%20looking%20forward%20to%20Tejashwi%20as%20a%20leader%20who%20can%20address%20their%20aspirations.%20He%20gave%20jobs%20to%20youths%20during%20his%20tenure%20as%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20and%20continuously%20talking%20about%20jobs%20as%20an%20opposition%20leader%20has%20worked%20in%20his%20favour%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftejashwi-yatra-bihar-bjp-desperate-to-change-headlines%5C%22%3EThreatened%20by%20Tejashwi%E2%80%99s%20Jan%20Vishwas%20Yatra%2C%20BJP%20Desperate%20to%20Change%20Headlines%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CUnemployment%20is%20a%20big%20issue%20for%20the%20youth%20and%20Tejashwi%20has%20created%20aspiration%20among%20them.%20Even%20in%20the%202020%20elections%2C%20he%20had%20established%20the%20employment%20narrative%2C%20due%20to%20which%20no%20other%20narrative%20worked%2C%20and%20other%20parties%20also%20had%20to%20talk%20about%20jobs%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20political%20analyst%20Mahendra%20Suman.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CTejashwi%20has%20given%20an%20initial%20blow%20to%20BJP%20and%20JDU%20by%20gathering%20a%20huge%20crowd%2C%20but%20it%20is%20too%20early%20to%20draw%20any%20conclusions%20from%20this%20crowd%20because%20a%20lot%20depends%20on%20what%20he%20does%20next%20after%20this%20yatra.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPatna-based%20journalist%20Amarnath%20Tiwary%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20remote%20villages%2C%20people%20do%20gather%20in%20large%20numbers%20if%20a%20political%20leader%20makes%20a%20visit.%20So%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20this%20crowd%20will%20convert%20into%20votes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ETejashwi%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20go%20beyond%20M-Y%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20yatra%20as%20well%20as%20in%20the%20mega%20rally%2C%20Tejashwi%20reiterated%20that%20RJD%20is%20the%20party%20of%20all%20sections%20of%20society%20and%20not%20only%20of%20Yadav%20and%20Muslim.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CRJD%20is%20not%20only%20the%20party%20of%20MY%20(Muslims%20and%20Yadavs)%20but%20also%20the%20party%20of%20BAAP.%20B%20means%20Bahujan%2C%20A%20means%20agra%20(forward%20classes)%2C%20A%20means%20adhi%20awaadi%20(women)%20P%20means%20poor%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20the%20mega%20rally%20in%20Gandhi%20Maidan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20the%20full%20form%20of%20RJD%20is%20Rights%2C%20Jobs%20and%20Development.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETejashwi%20has%20been%20attempting%20to%20make%20RJD%20a%20party%20of%20all%20castes%20and%20creeds%20for%20quite%20some%20time.%20In%20the%202020%20Bihar%20assembly%20elections%2C%20when%20he%20was%20the%20campaigner%20of%20mahagathbandhan%20and%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%2C%20Tejashwi%20had%20said%20that%20RJD%20is%20the%20party%20of%20%E2%80%98A%20to%20Z.%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20political%20analysts%20and%20journalists%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20party%20is%20yet%20to%20deliver%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98A%20to%20Z%E2%80%99%20combination%20in%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20see%20the%20selection%20of%20candidates%20in%20elections%2C%20you%20will%20not%20find%20that%20different%20caste%20groups%20are%20proportionately%20represented%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20Patna-based%20journalist%20Amarnath%20Tiwary%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuman%20said%20that%20if%C2%A0%20Tejashwi%20talks%20about%20social%20justice%2C%20it%20should%20be%20reflected%20in%20his%20decisions.%20%E2%80%9CUsing%20social%20justice%20as%20rhetoric%20will%20not%20help.%20They%20must%20put%20forward%20a%20clear%20blueprint%20for%20this.%20And%20he%20should%20also%20realise%20that%20social%20justice%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20empowering%20just%20one%20dominant%20caste.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20Patna-based%20journalist%20Santosh%20Singh%20says%20that%20making%20RJD%20acceptable%20to%20all%20parties%20is%20a%20process%20in%20progress%20but%20notes%20that%20there%20are%20challenges%20to%20attracting%20caste-neutral%20youths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%2C%20he%20is%20smart%20in%20talking%20about%20jobs%20for%20youths%20%E2%80%93%20caste-neutral%20issue.%20Tejashwi%20has%20started%20seeing%20youths%20as%20a%20possible%20constituency.%20This%20is%20working%20on%20the%20ground%20as%20well.%20He%20is%20getting%20traction%20among%20youths%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERamakant%20Chandan%2C%20a%20Patna%20based%20journalist%2C%20believes%20that%20upper%20castes%20are%20slowly%20turning%20to%20RJD.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTejashwi%20is%20targeting%20upper%20caste%20votes%20but%20also%20keeping%20grip%20on%20his%20core%20vote%20bank%20of%20M-Y%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chandan%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CUpper%20castes%E2%80%99%20viewpoint%20about%20RJD%20is%20changing.%20Upper%20castes%20may%20not%20be%20turning%20towards%20RJD%20in%20huge%20numbers%20but%20they%20are%20not%20hating%20the%20party%20as%20they%20were%20doing%20earlier%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709474108000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03192044%2FGHP5gulWQAIOIL_.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2F10-day-yatra-and-a-mega-rally-tejashwi-attempts-to-go-beyond-muslim-yadav-formula%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%9CRJD%20is%20not%20only%20the%20party%20of%20Muslims%20and%20Yadav%20but%20also%20the%20party%20of%20BAAP.%20B%20means%20Bahujan%2C%20A%20means%20agra%20(forward%20classes)%2C%20A%20means%20adhi%20awaadi%20(women)%20P%20means%20poor%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20said%20in%20the%20mega%20rally%20in%20Gandhi%20Maidan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2F10-day-yatra-and-a-mega-rally-tejashwi-attempts-to-go-beyond-muslim-yadav-formula%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hero%20police%20officer%20honoured%20after%20saving%20woman%20from%20blasphemy%20mob%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709470320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F03%2F768x432%2Fskynews-naqvi-pakistan-blasphemy_6477118.jpg%3F20240303125155%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhero-police-officer-who-saved-woman-from-blasphemy-mob-honoured-13086294%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20female%20police%20officer%20has%20been%20honoured%20for%20protecting%20a%20woman%20from%20a%20mob%20accusing%20her%20of%20blasphemy%20in%20Pakistan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A320%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhero-police-officer-who-saved-woman-from-blasphemy-mob-honoured-13086294%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhero-police-officer-who-saved-woman-from-blasphemy-mob-honoured-13086294%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhero-police-officer-who-saved-woman-from-blasphemy-mob-honoured-13086294%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farmer%20Unions%20Announce%20March%20Towards%20Delhi%20via%20Road%2C%20Air%2C%20Rail%20and%20on%20Foot%20on%20March%206%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15145529%2F9313A034-D5C5-4DE6-A64D-6FDBEE5AE65D-1.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EChandigarh%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20After%20the%20%3Cem%3Eantim%20bhog%3C%2Fem%3E%20ceremony%20of%20farmer%20Shubhkaran%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-protest-haryana-police-shubhkaran-singh%5C%22%3Ekilled%20during%20clashes%20between%20farmers%20and%20security%20forces%20last%20month%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20farmer%20bodies%20leading%20the%20%E2%80%98Delhi%20Challo%E2%80%99%20programme%20announced%20that%20they%20will%20be%20heading%20to%20the%20capital%20on%20March%206%20by%20train%2C%20bus%2C%20air%20and%20foot%20to%20step%20up%20pressure%20on%20the%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EJagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%2C%20convener%20of%20Samyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(SKM%20non-political)%2C%20who%20is%20leading%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20in%20Punjab%2C%20told%20the%20media%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20often%20asked%20farmers%20to%20march%20peacefully%20to%20Delhi%20without%20their%20tractor-trolleys.%20In%20line%20with%20this%2C%20the%20farmers%20have%20changed%20their%20strategy%20to%20reach%20Delhi%20through%20other%20means.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20now%20see%20how%20farmers%20are%20treated%20in%20Delhi%20and%20whether%20we%20are%20allowed%20to%20protest%20peacefully%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EDallewal%20also%20announced%20a%20one-day%20%E2%80%98rail-roko%E2%80%99%20program%20on%20March%2010%2C%20between%2012%20pm%20and%204%20pm%2C%20as%20part%20of%20their%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EHe%20appealed%20to%20the%20citizens%20of%20the%20country%20that%20this%20agitation%20is%20not%20of%20Haryana%2C%20Punjab%2C%20or%20Shubhkaran%20alone.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20national%20agitation%20and%20they%20must%20support%20their%20cause.%20He%20said%20this%20country%20will%20grow%20if%20farmers%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20legal%20guarantee%20to%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20(MSP)%20has%20been%20a%20key%20demand%20of%20farmer%20unions%2C%20which%20they%20claimed%20was%20promised%20by%20Modi%20government%20at%20the%20time%20of%20withdrawing%20three%20farm%20laws%20during%20last%20edition%20of%20farm%20protest%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3ESince%20the%20demand%20has%20remained%20unfulfilled%2C%20farmers%20unions%2C%20mainly%20splinter%20groups%20of%20SKM%20(which%20played%20key%20role%20in%202020%20farm%20protest)%20began%20marching%20towards%20Delhi%20on%20February%2013%20from%20various%20towns%20of%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EHowever%2C%20security%20forces%20deployed%20at%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%20borders%20at%20Shambhu%20and%20Khanauri%20halted%20their%20march%20by%20dropping%20tear%20gas%20shells%20and%20other%20excessive%20use%20of%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EIn%20several%20rounds%20of%20clashes%20since%20then%2C%20a%20large%20number%20of%20farmers%20as%20well%20as%20policemen%20have%20sustained%20serious%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EOne%20of%20them%20was%2022-year-old%20farmer%20Shubhkaran%20Singh%20from%20Bhatinda%E2%80%99s%20Ballo%20village%20who%20died%20during%20these%20clashes%20at%20Khanuari%20border%20on%20February%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EHis%20body%20was%20only%20cremated%20a%20week%20later%2C%20on%20February%2029%2C%20after%20Punjab%20police%20filed%20a%20murder%20case%20under%20pressure%20from%20farmer%20bodies.%C2%A0%20As%20per%20media%20reports%2C%20an%20autopsy%20report%20also%20confirmed%20the%20initial%20suspicion%20that%20he%20had%20died%20of%20a%20firearm%20injury%20on%20the%20back%20of%20his%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EStir%20to%20continue%20on%20borders%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Sarwan%20Singh%20Pandher%2C%20convener%20of%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Sangharsh%20Committee%2C%20which%20is%20also%20leading%20the%20Delhi%20Chalo%20march%2C%20also%20told%20media%20that%20their%20protest%20would%20continue%20at%20Punjab-Haryana%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20number%20of%20farmers%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20and%20Khannauri%20is%20set%20to%20increase%20in%20the%20coming%20days%2C%20while%20the%20remaining%20border%20points%20between%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20would%20also%20be%20covered%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EPandher%20said%20that%20there%20was%20no%20way%20that%20farmers%20will%20step%20back%20from%20their%20protest.%20They%20will%20fight%20till%20they%20get%20legal%20guarantee%20to%20MSP%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20is%20non-negotiable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20what%20would%20decide%20the%20fate%20of%20farmers%20in%20future.%20We%20can%E2%80%99t%20think%20of%20profitable%20farming%20until%20farmers%20are%20assured%20at%20least%20the%20price%20decided%20by%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20Pandher%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20large%20number%20of%20farmers%20attended%20the%20bhog%20ceramony%20at%20Shubhkaran%E2%80%99s%20native%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EAam%20Aadmi%20Party%20government%20in%20Punjab%20has%20declared%20Rs%201%20crore%20in%20compensation%20and%20a%20government%20job%20for%20the%20deceased%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20younger%20sister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPunjab%20BJP%20chief%20questions%20farmer%20leaders%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20BJP%20chief%20Sunil%20Jakhar%20said%20that%20all%20wheat%20and%20paddy%20produced%20in%20Punjab%20is%20being%20lifted%20at%20MSP%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%20%E2%80%9CThen%20whose%20battle%20are%20these%20so-called%20farmer%20leaders%20fighting%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20a%20guarantee%20of%20MSP%20will%20not%20solve%20the%20entire%20problem%20as%20none%20of%20the%20remaining%2021%20crops%20are%20as%20remunerative%20as%20paddy%20and%20wheat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20farmer%20leaders%20to%20tell%20what%20Punjab%20is%20to%20gain%20from%20this%20protest%20as%20we%20are%20already%20getting%20MSP%20on%20wheat%20and%20paddy%20which%20we%20produce%2C%20Jakhar%20said%2C%20asking%20asking%20farmer%20leaders%20not%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmislead%20youngsters%20from%20Punjab%20for%20their%20own%20motives.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709470068000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F1514