otha%2C%20to%20look%20at%20granting%20%E2%80%9Cconstitutional%E2%80%9D%20rights%20to%20the%20north-eastern%20state%E2%80%99s%20tribal%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20demand%20has%20a%20huge%20resonance%20across%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20tribal%20Tiprasas%20which%20form%2030%25%20of%20the%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsiderable%20credit%20goes%20to%20TIPRA%20Motha%20or%20the%20Tribal%20Indigenous%20People%E2%80%99s%20Regional%20Alliance%2C%20the%20newest%20and%20the%20most%20popular%20among%20the%20tribal%20parties%20of%20the%20state%2C%20for%20uniting%20the%20tribal%20political%20voice%20of%20Tripura%20towards%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20separate%20state%20culled%20out%20of%20the%20present%20geographical%20limits%20of%20the%20state.%20Unitedly%2C%20they%20have%20been%20staging%20a%20number%20of%20rallies%2C%20including%20at%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Jantar%20Mantar.%20TIPRA%20Motha%20also%20runs%20the%20tribal%20autonomous%20council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%201%2C%20in%20a%20clever%20move%2C%20TIPRA%20Motha%20chief%20Pradyot%20Debbarman%20held%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20state%20Congress%20and%20CPI(M)%20leaders%20for%20a%20possible%20alliance%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20has%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20one%20of%20which%20has%20a%20large%20number%20of%20tribal%20voters.%20In%20the%202014%20and%202019%20elections%2C%20both%20the%20seats%20were%20pocketed%20by%20the%20BJP.%20In%20the%202024%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20aiming%20at%20increasing%20its%202019%20tally%20of%2017%20of%20the%2025%20seats%20in%20the%20Northeast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20meeting%20in%20Agartala%2C%20Tripura%20Congress%20president%20Ashish%20Kumar%20Saha%20told%20reporters%20that%20his%20party%20expected%20TIPRA%20Motha%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftripura-congress-in-talks-with-tipra-and-cpim-for-alliance-in-lok-sabha-polls%2Farticle67900484.ece%5C%22%3Ejoin%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Opposition%20coalition%20in%20the%202024%20polls%20but%20was%20unsure%20of%20the%20regional%20party%E2%80%99s%20final%20stance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20then%2C%20Debbarman%20had%20announced%20sitting%20on%20a%20%E2%80%98fast%20unto%20death%E2%80%99%20to%20press%20the%20Centre%20to%20heed%20to%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20demand.%20He%20called%20all%20other%20Tiprasa%20leaders%20to%20join%20him%20also%20as%20it%20concerned%20the%20community%20in%20general.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20meeting%20the%20Opposition%20leaders%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%20invited%20Debbarman%20to%20visit%20New%20Delhi%20to%20seal%20a%20written%20agreement%20with%20the%20Centre%20to%20discuss%20in%20future%20granting%20of%20constitutional%20rights%20to%20the%20tribal%20population.%20Debbarman%20had%20been%20demanding%20a%20written%20agreement%20and%20not%20a%20verbal%20assurance%20from%20the%20Modi-Shah%20government%20on%20that%20count.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%202%2C%20a%20tripartite%20agreement%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D2010880%5C%22%3Ewas%20signed%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20MHA%20and%20the%20state%20government%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20Manik%20Saha%20%E2%80%9Cto%20amicably%20resolve%20all%20issues%20of%20the%20indigenous%20people%20of%20Tripura%20relating%20to%20history%2C%20land%20and%20political%20rights%2C%20economic%20development%2C%20identity%2C%20culture%20and%20heritage%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20after%20signing%20the%20agreement%2C%20termed%20it%20a%20%E2%80%98historic%20day%20for%20Tripura%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20pact%20is%20somewhat%20similar%20to%20the%20Framework%20Agreement%20signed%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20with%20the%20Naga%20leaders%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20to%20their%20political%20issue.%20The%20agreement%20with%20TIPRA%20Motha%20is%20aimed%20at%20weighing%20solutions%20to%20protect%20var