ue%20Journey%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20their%20unique%20products%2C%20what%20is%20interesting%20is%20the%20journey%20the%20founders%20had%20before%20collaborating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2039%2C%20Atul%E2%80%99s%20career%20started%20at%20the%20age%20of%2017.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20the%20youngest%20person%20in%20my%20batch%20to%20clear%20the%20Railways%20exams%20and%20got%20posted%20as%20a%20ticket%20collector.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20was%20acutely%20aware%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20lost%20their%20luggage%20to%20theft.%20I%20could%20see%20the%20distress%20and%20loss%20it%20caused%20to%20the%20people%20and%20had%20always%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20about%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F259714%2Fwest-bengal-history-woman-bela-mitra-brave-india-freedom-struggle-british-raj%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworking%20in%20the%20railways%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Atul%20also%20started%20to%20prepare%20for%20UPSC%20CSE%20to%20become%20a%20government%20servant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20not%20easy%20managing%20both%20things%20and%20I%20failed%20four%20times%20before%20cracking%20the%20exam%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20served%20as%20an%20officer%2C%20conducting%20audits%20of%20national%20Navratna%20companies%20and%20Maharatna%20PSUs%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%20This%20marked%20around%2013-14%20years%20into%20my%20service.%20While%20I%20enjoyed%20being%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333846%2Fhyderabad-balalatha-mallavarapu-affected-by-polio-crack-upsc-cse-without-coaching-teaches-aspirants%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecivil%20servant%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20yearned%20to%20create%20something%20of%20my%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdi