22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343305%2Fbest-local-food-in-hyderabad-recommendations-biryanj-andhra-meals-osmania-biscuit-nihari-paaya%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Beyond%20Bara%20Imambara%3A%20Heritage%20Photographer%20Captures%20Lucknow%E2%80%99s%20Hidden%20History%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAnyone%20who%20scrolls%20through%20Maroof%20Umar%E2%80%99s%20Instagram%20account%20is%20in%20for%20a%20visual%20feast.%20One%20reel%20in%20particular%20catches%20my%20attention%20%E2%80%94%20a%20huge%20metal%20pot%20simmering%20over%20a%20wood%20fire%20that%20has%20been%20built%20into%20the%20ground.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20is%20an%20attempt%20at%20telling%20the%20story%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3EDum%20Pukht%20Lucknowi%20Pulao%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20better%20known%20as%20the%20eponymous%20%3Cem%3EAwadhi%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Ebiryani.%20%3C%2Fem%3EIt%20is%20almost%20mesmerising%20to%20watch%20sliced%20onions%20find%20their%20way%20into%20the%20boiling%20oil%20as%20the%20meats%20patiently%20await%20their%20turn.%20Hindustani%20classical%20music%20accompanies%20the%20ensuing%20steps%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343137%2Fbengaluru-rameshwaram-cafe-started-by-iim-grad-divya-raghav-rao-podi-masala-dosa-idli-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20recipe%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20every%20beat%20announcing%20the%20next%20addition%20to%20the%20dish.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20coming%20together%20of%20the%20ingredients%20is%20captured%20so%20brilliantly%2C%20that%20when%20the%20lid%20is%20finally%20taken%20off%20the%20sealed%20pot%2C%20I%20find%20my%20mouth%20watering%20at%20the%20outcome%20that%20will%20soon%20meet%20the%20camera%E2%80%99s%20eye.%20Few%20photographers%20can%20capture%20the%20elusive%20moments%20of%20magic%20in%20something%20as%20routine%20as%20%3Cem%3Ebiryani%3C%2Fem%3E%20preparation.%20One%20of%20them%20is%20Maroof.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20been%20spinning%20enchanting%20narratives%20around%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F339785%2Frepublic-day-ministry-of-culture-ananta-sutra-celebrates-legacy-of-sari-weaves-kartavya-path%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20cultural%20lores%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20years%20with%20his%20Sony%20%CE%B17S%20III%20camera%20as%20his%20steadfast%20companion.%20From%20a%20college%20dropout%20to%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20loved%20heritage%20storytellers%20%E2%80%94%20with%20over%20three%20lakh%20followers%20and%20counting%20%E2%80%94%20Maroof%E2%80%99s%20journey%20is%20fascinating.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20candour%20towards%20fame%20and%20love%20for%20his%20craft%20is%20evident%20as%20he%20gets%20chatting%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%E2%80%9CLike%20any%20artist%2C%20I%20look%20for%20happiness%20in%20my%20work%3B%20the%20food%20I%20taste%2C%20and%20the%20people%20I%20meet.%20If%20I%20look%20back%20at%20the%20graph%20of%20my%20happiness%20over%20the%20years%20it%20has%20always%20been%20a%20constant.%20The%20little%20things%20made%20me%20happy%20when%20I%20started%20and%20they%20continue%20to%20do%20so.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20while%20Maroof%20has%20found%20fame%20in%20diligently%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338686%2Ffreedom-fighter-gandhian-india-best-railway-minister-madhu-dandavate-rail-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earchiving%20India%E2%80%99s%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20was%20never%20the%20original%20plan%2C%20he%20shares.%20Months%20into%20a%20commerce%20course%2C%20he%20figured%20the%20traditional%20academic%20route%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20for%20him%20and%20he%20dropped%20out%20to%20start%20a%20design%20agency%20in%202012.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20visual%20arts%20had%20always%20intrigued%20me.%20I%E2%80%99d%20always%20viewed%20the%20world%20from%20a%20different%20perspective%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20agency%20was%20on%20its%20feet%2C%20Maroof%20says%20there%20was%20a%20deeper%20calling%20he%20had.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20explore%20my%20city%20and%20tell%20the%20stories%20it%20held%20within%20its%20walls.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202048px)%20100vw%2C%202048px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG_1294-2_11zon-1709040825-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maroof%20Umar%20is%20a%20heritage%20storyteller%20who%20chronicles%20the%20history%20and%20culture%20of%20Lucknow%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG_1294-2_11zon-1709040825-scaled.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG_1294-2_11zon-1709040825-240x300.jpg%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG_1294-2_11zon-1709040825-500x625.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG_1294-2_11zon-1709040825-768x960.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG_1294-2_11zon-1709040825-1229x1536.jpg%201229w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG_1294-2_11zon-1709040825-1638x2048.jpg%201638w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG_1294-2_11zon-1709040825-150x188.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343318%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMaroof%20Umar%20is%20a%20heritage%20storyteller%20who%20chronicles%20the%20history%20and%20culture%20of%20Lucknow%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%2