childhood%20milestones%20they%20may%20not%20become%20aware%20of%20potential%20hearing%20issues%20until%20around%20the%20time%20the%20child%20reaches%20two%20years%20of%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20advancements%20in%20healthcare%20and%20technology%2C%20newborn%20hearing%20screenings%20can%20now%20detect%20hearing%20loss%20much%20before%20even%20the%20earliest%20milestones-based%20diagnosis.%20These%20screenings%20aid%20in%20the%20early%20detection%20of%20hearing%20problems%2C%20allowing%20for%20follow-up%20consultations%20with%20paediatricians%20within%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20first%20two%20to%20three%20months%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20estimates%20that%20there%20are%2063%20million%20people%20in%20India%20who%20suffer%20from%20significant%20auditory%20impairment.%20It%20further%20notes%20that%20up%20to%20five%20out%20of%20every%201%2C000%20babies%20are%20born%20with%20hearing%20loss%20or%20acquire%20it%20soon%20after%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20key%20to%20effective%20management%20of%20hearing%20loss%20is%20early%20identification%20and%20prompt%20treatment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChildren%20experiencing%20mild%20to%20moderate%20hearing%20loss%20can%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F63445%2Fhearing-impairments-balavidyalaya-school-chennai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebenefit%20from%20hearing%20aids%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20those%20with%20profound%20hearing%20loss%2C%20Cochlear%20Implants%20(CI)%20offer%20a%20solution.%20These%20electronic%20devices%20serve%20to%20replace%20the%20function%20of%20the%20damaged%20inner%20ear%2C%20facilitating%20the%20sense%20of%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20enables%20children%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20auditory%20world%20and%20lead%20lives%20similar%20to%20other%20children%20in%20every%20aspect.%20However%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20Cochlear%20Implant%20(CI)%20surgery%20is%20expe